There are people who say, no matter how long you live, but what counts is how you live.
So as for them, the quality of life is something what really matters.
It would be hard to deny it, but on the other hand our desire to live is so strong and obvious that we are eager to extend the life span every possible way.
In the first place, there are a lot of advantages of leading peaceful and long life.
The longer you live the more opportunity to share your time with your love ones such as friends and family.
Each day has its uniqe importance and beauty.
People have possibility to learn something new day in day out what makes the life purposeful and meaningful.
But there are people eager to push their limits and try whatever possible in their lives.
They set themselves some goals and feel the tremor of excitement when achieving them.
For example: they want to see the ocean and learn how to dive in its deep water and they are convinced in the heart of heart that only if they gain it, they will truly feel fulfill and exhilarated.
Such people would not like boring and quiet live without risky and adventurous situations.
If I had to choos I would go for longer and calm life to enjoy the life and people I love day by day, taking advantegous of each single joy.
