In this decades,we ran into many innovations that was affected by technology.
Many of them is got used easily by people because the producers of those products has been providing new models in our lives in every years such as computers,tablets or smartphones.
People get adopt to those device and use whole time of their lives.
Hence companies increase their sales number.
Everyone is grateful to technology and they do not want to turn back to old techniques like books,magazines or newspaper.
For example,nowadays children prefer computer,tablets or internet to learn something,so that situation reminds us this question \u201C Should computers and tablets remove books in education areas of study ? \u201D
In generally,technology has lot of magnificent benefits.
If we talk about educational stations,it has more.
For instance,tablets and e-reader very useful for student because you can find out or take note anything what do you want without pen.
It stores as much information as 3 or 4 libraries does have books.
Simple,quick and useful.
Furthermore,using that product is a good way to against deforestation because every year many trees cut down to publish a book.
On the other hand,many scientist suggest that books are a good guide to learn because when you look up any information but can not see quickly review,you have to keep to scanning until you find.
So,you have more chance to memorize after you finish your searching.
In my opinion,two sides has good benefits but I support that books should still be in school and universities.
Before to pass technological innovations,every people should try old techniques to learn any information.
