Telling the truth Most of the people I know believe that you should never tell a lies,which is completely correct and understandable.
Nevertheless, in my personal opinion it is not always possible to tell only the truth.
In some cases I even believe that it is acceptable to tell a lie.
Some lies can save you from bad situations.
Complex situations need complex resolutions.
Other lies can help you to achieve your goals,but I do not support these kind of lies,because it is not right to lie in order to get what you want.
This is just rude and unfair towards people who are trying to achieve their goals too,but without lies as a normal,good human-beings.
I would like to give you some examples of situations in which I feel like it is acceptable to lie.
There are not many of them,but they exist.
The first situation is when you are in direct danger and someone is threatening you.
For example when you called the police,but when they ask you if you called someone ,you say that you did not call anyone.
Because if you would say the truth, you would put yourself even in bigger danger.
The second situation is when you do not want to hurt someone.
You heard your bestfriend gossiping about your sister and because you do not want to hurt your sister\u00B4s feeling you do not tell her about it.
She would be extremely upset by it.
But generally I agree that lies are bad.
I think the follwing three things may be more important than exercise for our health.
The first is diet.
We have to eat a meal to get good nutritions like a protein, a fat and vitamins and so on.
Because the nutrition is the source of power,We can not move our body perfectly without good diet.
The second is rest especially sleeping.
If you run short of sleep,you can not control your body and your mind correctly.
Besides short sleep is bad for your health because your immune system weaken.
Third I think the most important for our health is keeping good mental conditions.
First of all you have to keep your mental health if you want to get good phisical health.
To get good mental conditions,you should maintain your thought.
You should sometimes refresh your mind for exmple playing with friends or drinking or having dinner with your family and so on.
A good health is whrere a good mental conditions.
