Since the date of its invention, television has become even more important in our life.
In fact, we love it because it is able to entertain us.
Many people claim that watching television is unhealty and useless.
However, it can also teach you something.
Children also spend time on television.
While it is true that there are programmes for children which are poor of quality, there are some good cartoons which are educative: children may learn a foreign language from them or you can find programmes which teach vital values such as friendship and loyalty.
Obviously, parents must limit the time their children spend watching TV.
Moreover, there are also wonderful programme for grown-up people.
The might concern sport, and there are programmes about cooking.
In addition, there are programmes about health, politics, economics and so on.
Documentaries are also good programmes.
They are about all types of science, so they can be very interesting.
However, in my view, too few people watch documentaries, also because they are not advertised enough.
To sum up, TV programmes can be good or dreadful: it is up to you to do the best choice.
It is widespread and common that people think it is no problem to lie once or more often.
Other people think differently and are convinced that telling the truth is one of the most important things.
In the following I am going to explain my opinion wether lying is acceptable or not.
In my opinion is telling the truth a very important thing.
It is a great character trial which many people have lost.
I believe in the bible which is telling me that lying comes from the devil.
The devil is the biggest lyer on earth.
It means lying is not acceptable for God.
The question is why.
For sure, first lying looks not like a problem.
It has also advantages to lie.
When I did not make my homework and my teacher wants me to read them out, it may be logical that I lie and say that I do not find them or however.
And even if other people ask me something about a secret for example and I cannot tell them, then it is also common that people lie.
Is that not understandable?
Sure, it is hard to answer.
Especially when it is not just about my advantage but about others.
But all in all I would still think that lying is not the best way.
Actually you can hurt people with lying and lying because of loving, can not be the way.
Who loves, tells the truth.
I am convinced that telling the truth is a good way to improve the wolrd.
How many problems are created, just because people decided to lie?
Yes, it is not acceptable.
Lying is sin.
