I know from my experiences that exercising is vital part of human life.
It is not just about beeing physical fit.
It is much deeper.
Ofcourse, if you are fit, most of the things are easier for you, you feel better and you even feel better about yourself and it improves your life.
But it is not the most important part for me.
What I see as the key aspect of excercising is improving your mental strenght.
You have to suffer to grow.
Nothing easy can make you better and if you can do something physicaly demanding every day, you can improve your brain and make yourself stronger and better.
You can use it it aspects of everyday life.
You need to get aout of your comfort zone and feel the pain and most importantly to handle it.
And the best way to do it is by excercising.
So, I doubt that you can find something really more important becouse excercise is basic part of your life and you need proper basics.
I am an Englsih learner who is doing all his best to pass the Cambridge C1 exams, and I always look for every tool that can help me to get my goal.
I jumped into a new internet site where is given the opportunity to make some improvents, especially in the part where students are weaker.
This is because i am practicing some types of writings with the help of the new site I discovered.
The site seems well-managed and it gives all the tools whose use is expected to get satisfacting results.
The main feature I appreciate is to choose what kind of writing I want to practise: an essay, a report or an article, in other words all the tasks that I could be required writing.
It should not be forgotten the section "task timer" that makes you sure about the time you are spending in every single writing so that you can organise your time in a free-risk manner.
however, I must admit I have some difficulties for example when I must decide which task to do, and it depends on the lenght of the title task; it would be better a shorter one.
On the whole, I strongly reccomend to enter the site, making the registration process and being patient before seeing all the improvements you want to make.
Hard study is the successfull key.
There are no doubts about its usefullness, tasks are sending to an examiner who will write you back the corrections and the stressed mistakes.
