However, for me, there is more than this side of a coin.
First I want to travel a lot and the language needed is English.
Of course, other languages would be useful as well.
Still I think that English is the most important one.
Due to the many people who have at least a basic knowledge in speaking or writing English it is the mos required language.
Communicating necessary both in private life and in the world of work.
Therefore, do not let anyone stop you from learning English and always try your best!
