That is why everyone should have at least some music in school.
Music is not necesarily a subject you get a grade on, but more of a group building free time activity.
There should not be any restrictions, so that teachers can create individual experiences for every class.
I am sure, that music has a good influence on everyone's health and it could also help to prevent illnesses.
For example burn-out, which is common among pupils, could be elliminated.
Therefore, everyschool should offer some music courses!
