Today I have just seen the most emotional and beautiful movie ever.
It is called Me Before You.
It is about Will who had a motor accident, which left him with a spinal cord injury.
That is why he needed to be taken care of.
Louisa took up the job to take care of him, but they dislike each other.
Then Louisa overheard a conversation between Will's parents, that he didn't want to live anymore.
She decided to make a plan to let Will see how beautiful life is.
During the vacation they fell in love, but Will decided to choose for euthanasia.
When Will died, he left her a letter and it was the most beautiful letter I have ever seen.
Kind regards Leanne Klaver
