Studying abroad give student the oppurtinity to see the world, because as I mention earlier you will in contact students and teachers with different background.
This will bring many advantageous for students, because as we know we live a world where globalization is accelarating.
Some companies ask abroad exprience.
So, in a globalized job market it is very important to have international exprience.
Different studies show that student who followed abroad study have more chance to find a within six month than those who don not have this exprience.
Furthermore knowledge of different cultural will help you to communicate with all types of people.
