So I will talk about it.
My most favourite holiday was in the summer in 2019.
I was in a school's Physics team.
In this team, we learn too much about Physics, it's really hard, to join Physics competitions and get awards.
And we got a support from my school, they provided money for us to learn in High School for Gifted in Ho Chi Minh City.
Of course, we moved to Sai Gon in that summer.
In that time, we learn Physics with a excellence teacher name Pham Hoang and his class on the morning.
It is the worst mornings in my life.
He taught the things that I can't absolutely understand anything.
But after that, everything with me was like heaven.
I had all time in the afternoon and everning to do anything I like.
Usually, we would have lunch after learing time and go back to BK Dorm, took a nap to 3 p.m.. And then, sometime we went to the mall together, somtime just stayed in our own room, played guiter, sang and told stories.
And until 5p.m., I went to sport room and played table tennis with students in BKU.
I met some new friends, they all were really kind and friendly.
And it was my best holiday.
