The purpose of this report is to tell you my writing experience with Write and Improve.
Firstly, I really appreciate how fast Write and Improve can check my works, give a feedback backward and evaluate my writing skill.
Another fact to consider is this program is totally free therefore everybody can use it and I must also mention that I can use this program at any time, which means I can practice my writing as much as I want.
However, inspite of the fact that is well-programmed, I would rather having a person who can give more advice and explaination, even though it is already clear. Such as examples, synonyms.
To sum up, I have no hesitation in recommending Write and Improve to my friends, because it really helps me to improve my English and be more confident in using English words.
Otherwise, they would not improve.
You would not believe that one of the most important holiday I have ever had was the one when my sister got married and I was the bridesmaid.
It was in Thailand and believe or not, there is nothing in the world like this wedding.
For a start, the organisation was well-planned.
Every detail was perfectly neat, such as the choice of flowers and meals.
I must also mention that there was an orchestra for the reception.
The choice of music was selected by the maid and do you know what, everybody was full of emotion, particularly my parents.
Apart from that, the theme of the wedding was about Thailand, therefore every guests were wearing traditional uniform and it was proudful.
Personnally, I believe that my sister's wedding was one of the best holiday I have ever had because it was full of joy and tears.
Unfortunately, I had to get back to Switzerland two days after but I would remember that party forever.
