I am going to describe my experience with Write and Improve.
To begin with, I totally like it with four reasons.
Firstly, its variety of topics.
Since I can face to many kinds of topics, I improve my writing skill wider and wider.
Secondly, its marking speed.
As soon as I push the check button, it mark and correct my writings.
It does save time a lot.
Thirdly, its score history.
I can see my past grades.
It allows me to know how I improve my writing skill and stay motivated.
Lastly, its design.
It is very tidy and helpful to go around the site.
However, I have one dislike point.
It is its correction degree.
It is very hard to understand where or how I can correct my writings to make it better one.
It adds shades to the sentences, but not helpful.
I want it to add more detail notes to my writings.
Finally, I really rely on this service.
I reccomend you to start useing it.
