What is the most important thing our life?
We have a lot of different answers for this question.
Somebody says the money, lots of money another people says happy family,...
For me, the important and precious thing in our life is healthy.
I guess there are a lot of people think like me but most of them don't care their health much, especially the young people like university students and school children.
I'm also a school student, so I will understand a part of young people thinking and the things they care much.
Before, I was a lazy person about take care of myself, especially exercise and health, I had just concentrated about study, my goals and the way I could achieved these.
I used to hate do exercise in the morning very much because I thought it wasted my precious time.
Even my mother always reminded me do exercise or play some sports.
But I often ignored them.
Then some little proplem about health came to me.
Suddenly, I realized my faults in that time and I started care about my health much than before.
There are a lot of reason for us to concern our health,especially do more exercise at least 3 times a week.
Firstly, the health is the most important thing in our life.
Our parants gave birth us very strong,have a good health, so we must have responsibility to protect our health through do exercise, play sports, change our bad habits and also lifestyle.
Secondly, bad lifestyle affects our yield of work and study.
We always feel tired, exhausted and don't have energy to continue the work.
Finally, we usually unconscious, so we will have negative thinking and give the decission not good.
So young people should play the sports at least 3 times a week.
We will have feel betterand have more energy after each training session.
We also have a lot of friends.
It will improve relationships.
There are alot of benefits when we play the sports.
