Hello everybody, I'm Nael !
Today I will talk you about a website for learners of English.
Many people say this is so hard to find a great website or a great tool to learn english but today I will present you the best website to improve your abilities and skills in english when you are beginner or confirmed.
His name is Write and Improve, this website was created by Cambridge University in 2016, he his free and he is very easy to access.
First of all, in this website you can write about many subject as global warming or your favorite hobbies according to each level and when you have finish a robot check all your answers and he show you all your right and wrong answers.
After that you can see your evolution and be better than yesterday, you can practice yourself every time and also be more confident when you right in English.
Personally, I have used "Write and Improve" since two months and I can see a very big progression between when I started and now, I have also increase my vocabulary and I'm able to right an email.
I recommend you "write and and improve" for many reasons but if I have to choose only one to come here , It will be because it's pretty easy to learn in "Write and improve " and do not forget, study is the worth thing you have to do.
Firstly, Write and Improve provides me the opportunity to write English.
If you carry on every day, it is meant to improve your English writing skill.
Learning English is sometimes quite solitaly so it could be helpful to receive the correct sentences.
Secondly, Write and Improve corrects my wrong words and wired sentences.
We, Japanese, are careless of articles so much because this idea never exists in Japanese.
Meanwhile, there are many intricated words which have similar meaning, thus we also struggle to find out appropriate words in each sentences.
I think the native speakers feel that Japanese English is wired.
We sometimes really don't know which word is correct case by case basis.
However, Write and Improve teaches me the correct word in my sentences.
Finally, I got to look up these intricated words in the dictionary.
Write and Improve encourages me to learn English deep inside.
Therefore, I strongly recommend my classmates to try Write and Improve and keep English practice.
