A NEW SCHOOL YEAR Introduction The purpose of this report is to think and plan my new school year including things that I already achived, subjects that I can improve and establish new goals to avhieve during the year.
My comfortable areas of study Since I was really small, I'm good at mathematics, English and Geography.
I have always been keen on that subjects so my plan for these year, although it will be a little bit more complicated than last year, is to mantain that level.
Improving subjects On the other hand, I'm used to struggle in areas like Spanish language, phisics or arts, so during this course I'll try to give more attention to that things in order to get better marks so the next year won't be that difficult.
Motivation and effort Finally, encouragement and endeavour, these are going to be the keys for me this year .
Working really hard during the school time and relaxing on holidays are my plans so that I can achieve all my aims.
Moreover, beeng organised and constant are indispensable too.
Conclusion If you really work hard you can get whatever you want, all you need is willpower.
At the end, you will be proud of what you have achieved, so I'm feeling really confident and elated to start this new year.
