I want to tell you more about a new tool I discoverded lately.
As I am myself a learner of English, I am always looking for new supports that can be instructive.
Being curious is in my opinion the first step to achieve something, and looking for a solution by yourself is an excellent way to go.
So, let me tell you more about my founding: Write and Improve.
To start, I will describe you the main features of the tool, and how usefulll it is.
Write and Improve is an easy way to improve your writting english skills.
The website is nice and you go straigh to the point.
On the main page you will have a certain amount of subjects which will be graduate regarding the english level (for example: advanced).
Then you will write about the sujected you chose.
When you have completed your argumentation you can check your result imediatly.
And guess what ?
Within a minute you can have interesting feedbacks thanks to artificial intellengency.
Your text is highlighted where something doesn't seems right, and it gives you your acadamic level (A,B,C) right away.
You can then correct it to improve.
Write and Improve is adaptative to any level, so everyone is welcomed to try, and you don't even need to sign in to access it.
Of course it is better in my opinion because you can follow your tracks, and your improvement from day yo day.
I only wish there woud be more test to take !
Anyway I recommand it !
