I accidentally stumbled upon 'write and Improve', while searching online for English courses .
I have to say that I am very happy that it happend. '
Write and Improve' is an usefull and free tool for improving your English.
It provides random topics and task for practising your writing.
You can easily choose your level in which you would like to improve.
It various from beginner (A1) to Business (C2).
You even have a 'Just for fun' section.
The site is very easy to use.
This makes it really accessible for everyone.
When you finish your assignment, the application will immediately check your tekst on grammar.
It will afterwards provide you with additional feedback.
A ranking (A1-C2) of your skill is also provided.
The application gives you than the option, for improving your work.
You can resent (recheck) your work after improving it.
A diagram shows your progression while practsing.
There is only one small thing that could improve.
You will somtimes get an orange highlight on a sentence.
But it is never very clear what it means.
You have to figure it out by yourself.
Additional feedback would be nice.
I would definitely adviese ' Write and Improve" to everyone who wants to practis his or her Englisch writing.
It is easy, free and quick.
