You will get independence: your parents won't be with you, for that reason, you are going to learn to solve the problems by yourself.
2.
You will get new cultural habirs: in other countries there are many different habits which will enrich your knowledge and behavior.
3.
More opportunites to get a better job when you come back to your home country, in comparison with the rest of people.
