Speaking is thinking.
The way of how people think can be measured by their spoken words.
If people tell a lie, they cannot be trusted.
Lying is an acceptable action, except in emergency condition.
Always tell the truth is important.
By always saying the truth, the people could obtain the trust.
Trust from the people is one of the important in life.
When we study at university or work at compay, obtaining trust is a top priority once we entered new environment.
Lying, in opposite, will make us in marginal zone at which we can easily be dropped off from that zone.
Telling the truth is also safer than telling a lie.
Although it is difficult to tell the truth in some conditions, telling the real case not only makes us unloaded physically but also mentally.
The habit to telling the truth, without any addition and deduction, will strengthen quality of life.
True data will deliver right decision.
In contrast, fake data will result in wrong decision.
It is a case when telling a lie is an acceptable action.
A lie can be accepted when someone in danger and telling the truth will put their safety in danger.
In this case, the only way is to tell a lie.
Nevertheless, everything should be explained in truth once the problem is solved.
