Even though you can versatile in cold or hot weather, weather is also one thing you have to face with if you study aboard. For instance, she is coming from hot weather (Myanmar) to the United Kingdom, facing to cold weather about minus degree Celsius. Just round a year, she will get used to it. If you come to the United Kingdom, you apply to Uni by international student which is expensive about British Pound 30000 to 50000.
And another disadvantage is that, just depend on your abilities and backgrounds, you must prepare to enroll to the university such as IELTS or TOEFL, Maths and Sciences, depend on your specialization.
On the other hand, besides that, it is mentioned that study in overseas can make your progress such as languages skills, you might be bilingual or multilingual.
