Living in safe zone can not make you progress, do not coward, follow your aims which would be better in future.
I am using Write and Improve about 12 days and I really feel the improvement when I am writing new essays.
As the positive aspects of this platform, I can mention that I have become more aware of the vocabularies dictation and their use in the text.
Also, I am trying to use the appropriate collocations and writing a little bit longer sentences.
Furthermore, my progress motivates me to not give up and do not underestimate small steps toward success in writing a high-quality essay.
On the other hand, I think the website needs to be more specific about the candidate mistakes and gives a better suggestion.
For example, I searched about one of the collocations that the website detects it as a mistake, and I found that it was right.
Maybe it was about that collocation could not be embedded in that topic.
Generally, Write and improve website has been very helpful for me until now and I recommend you to use it on a daily basis.
The consistency in the writing practising and track your progress is the key factor to gain a higher score in IELTS writing.
