I find this topic interesting.
I have never given a thought about it but i have my own choice related to the office furnitures for employees.
I am listing the important points which should be considered for finalizing the type of office design that are most appropriate for employess.
These are:- 1) As employees sit with their coworkers, adequate distance must be maintained.
2) Two employees who are sitting adjacently are not able to see each other computers or works.
3) All employees can be seen from one end.
4) Hall should be airy enough for maintainig good hyigenic.
5) People who are dealing with clients must have sitting arrangements infront of them.
6) Sufficient space between two workstations must be maintained.
Considering the all points as mentioned above, we can think of better design of office furniture.
I will suggest the design which has two desks i.
e.,
two employees can work simultaneously.
Both desks are adjacent to each other but separated by wall.
Each desk has chair for clients in front of the employees.
By providing the sufficient gap between the tables, optimum space can be utilized in the hall and office will be airy enough at the same time.
