I am going to outline about the most significant holiday I have ever had.
What make me say that was the best holiday because in this essay I am exploring about.
Firstly, my young age life experience was not smooth road due to the fact that I have been staying with my parternal aunty and uncle in Myanmar (Yangon). Because my parents have been earning money at Taiwan so, I have a few chance to meet with them once in five years.
When I was young, the technology have not improved so far.
Nowadays, you can keep in touch with every countries of friends and family with internet applications such as messenger, viber and wechat etc.
I did not use to know about my parents care, warm, sweet-heart, patient and stuck with loneliness, monotonous and cold.
I wish I could have to stay with my parents everyday is my dream.
However, my dreams were come true because I was got a chance to go to my parents exist where is Taiwan.
Taiwan is the heart of Asia with pack of skyscrapers among that Taiwan 101is the tallest and most breathtaking also include in the world tallest buildings top ten.
Another famous place are the night market, shopping districts, bubble tea, Chinese cuisines and snacks.
I had had cloud nine to go to Taiwan, I get there it is more sensational than I expected.
My parents came to the Taoyuan airport and waited to meet me, when I was seeing them, I ran and embraced with them.
I have almost stayed with them about 5 or 6 months and had very awesome experience in my life.
I hung out with them such as shopping, eating and playing some games.
When I have to go back to Myanmar, they gave to me so many souvenirs, snacks, gadgets and by the way, I got a iPhone present from my mother.
As, in the nutshell, that holiday was the most exciting and tremendous experience in my life.
I hope I will be planning to go back to Taiwan to meet my parents again.
