The best holiday of my life was 10 years ago.
My family and I went to Portugal for a week.
Evidently, Portugal is a great holiday destination because of the landscape and the ocean.
Still, there is another reason why it is my favourity trip.
Since I was a little girl, I dreamed of swimming with a dolphin once.
This dream came true during our holidays in Portugal.
A few days after we arrived, we visited a water park called "Zoomarine."
The park itself was already pretty fun.
There were various water slides and you could watch different sea animal shows.
However, the best about this park was the possibility to swim with dolphins.
After a short instruction we were able to join them in their pool.
I even had the opportunity to swim with one of them alone.
As you can see, this was an experience I was looking forward to a lot.
As a result, this was the best holiday ever and even one of the best moments in my whole life.
