There are always arguments about zoos: by one side they're really apreciated, especially by children, by the other they're strongly criticized, especially by young people and animalists.
Certainly, zoos shouldn't exist in the way they actually do.
We always see animals living in places - or to better say cages - within really different conditions from their original habitats.
Animals seem to live in another world, far away from our reality.
They often have attonished expressions, like if they have been hypnotized.
They look tired and their movements are extremely slow.
Captivity denies them their natural freedom and makes them like dolls to admire behind a glass.
I've been taken to zous too when I was a child, and sometimes I've visited them more recently.
When I was a child I was excited - as it is normal a child is - to see animals I didn't even know existed, but right now I understand that it's not good.
In the Orecchiella Park there are six hursas loked in 60 square metres cages under the sun.
They seem to be suffering hotness of the summer quite a lot.
Animals in zoos also looose their predator's abilities because they always get food both from visitors - who gave them food despite the denies - and zoo's employees.
I agree more with safaries and natural parks, because animals which live in there can benefice of better conditions and walk and run in bigger spaces, often pretty similar to their natural habitats.
It is clear that the future of travel their own have different and same.
In this essay, I am going to demonstrate about different and same.
Based on my knowledge, there will be having four main sources of traveling systems such as bus (coach), normal train or underground, airway and cruise.
Coach system is almost nearly the perfect that is why there is no way to changing a lot.
Even though normal train system is slow, farmers, cultivation person and who stay in outskirts person are relied on that due to the fact that it is cheap and accurate.
Underground railway is absolutely accomplished, will not change in future.
Most people believe that there will become supersonic speed train appears soon.
On the other hand, airway system will not be dead because we all rely on the aircraft to travel aboards.
Some of scientists are planning to anouncement about gigantic aircraft, faster speed and could allow to board more than one hundred people.
And last, but not least, cruise is also support a main in transportation.
I read some article in newspaper, cruise will have more luxurious such as play grounds, swimming pools and shopping centers etc and also more fast, accurate than past.
Secondly, hotels are the biggest changing in the future.
Instead of human there are planning to replace with robots.
For instance, China, some pricey restaurants, especially hotpot, if you order some side dishes, they come with robots and serve on your tables.
And another example, in Japan, hotel staff are running with all robots, can show you which room did you reservation and give your some lunch, dinner box and morning breakfast.
My personal point of view, food will be changing consequently, the traditional cuisine are replacing with fast food which it is the most I concern.
As, in the nutshell, I think following things will be changing in the near future.
