To improve my English writing I've started using an on-line platform called "write&Improve."
It has been really useful to me, because I finally had the chance to get my writing checked.
My opinion about this platform is very positive.
I found it extremely easy to use, very intuitive.
The layout is clear and linear.
Write&Improve offers exercises of several difficulty levels: everyone can pratice using this platform.
There are excercises for beginners, for intermediate ones and for advanced ones.
It is also possibile to develop our English business skills.
I found very interesting the possibility to get back on my past writing to try make them better.
Checking process is very fast and it is the most useful part of the platform.
I could verify my ortographical mistakes and correct them.
There are also two colors which highlit that maybe a certain sentence can be written in a different and more fluid way.
About this point I have to underline the only difect I found: when the algorythm find a speach not correct, it doesn't suggest a correct way to improve it.
