Some people believe that employees work in enclosed work stations or open design stations their own have benefits and drawbacks.
In this essay I am going to outline two main reasons of enclosed work stations or cubicles and open design stations.
Based on my knowledge, I am going to demonstrate advantage about enclosed work stations or cubicles.
If she do that kind of work stations, her employees will have more space and can put anything's they want such as some snacks, water bottles and personal things.
Recently, every countries have to face with Noval coronavirus, everyone have to stay distance.
Enclosed work stations can easily defend that virus due to the fact that it is more distance and who has less chance to keep in touch with people.
However, there are not only need space but also need fortunes to make rooms, which need air-conditionals or ventilation fans to clean the office air fresh.
They have to communicate with some acquaintance workers and colleagues by phone.
Besides that It is mentioned that upsides of open design stations.
They can communicate, help each other without any phones or technical devices.
The work stations is open design, air could circulation and can get more fresh air.
From employer, she need to rent only small place where can also do so many office desks and not need a lot of exhaust fans and air-conditionals.
On the other hand, employees are might not get personal space and if she put some experience things like mobile phone, she have to take care of that.
Nowadays, Noval coronavirus infect with a least 20m which someone get with it, everybody will infect within 20 seconds.
As, in the nutshell, that following parts are upsides and downsides of enclosed work stations and open design stations.
It is just depend on the personal preference which stations are more effective.
