Let mi introduce my point of view.
It is important to say that I am studying military university and it is a bit different education system.
Our military university is part of our defence forces so it prepares soldiers for their duty.
With that you are not allowed to study foreign civil university.
So if you want to study abroad you had to choos some of the military schools.
It is true that it can be useful to know tactics of other armies.
But we are offered to study only in countries like Austria.
Their armed forces are not equal to ours at all.
I don't belive that czech soldier can profit from such education.
In my opinion the only reason why students want to study foreign military university is just entertiment and money.
We are studying important things about our future job every day.
It fits to our forces.
You can't learn such things somewhere else and you can't catch up with the rest of the class.
It is becaouse you will miss some important practical lessons.
The main reason is obviously Money because thats what makes everyone doing something, also there is the disadvantage of only contact with old patients that need more attention than the others.
People think that money gives happiness.
I personally think that being healthy is much more valuable and important.
First of all, money can buy a lot and make your life easier , however it will not buy your health.
In my opinion we should be physically active as much as possible and try to find that spare 30 min for exceesice at least 3 times a week.
Nowadays, processed, unhealthy food, stressful situations, pollution and busy day to day life can affect our wellness.
And money cannot change it.
But we can by simply eating healthier, changing bad habits, avoiding fast foods.
Personally, I think that being healthy means much more to me than being rich.
I believe that I can prevent poor health conditions by active lifestyle.
To sum up, I truly believe that being healthy is more important than being rich.
I person would love to live as long as possible to see my children and future grandchildren grow and to make memories of those priceless moments which money could not buy.
