In my opinion, computers and tables can replace books in schools and univeristy.
Firstly, children are grow up with electronic devices which become natural environment of their grow up.
As a result books are for them oldfashion and boring.
They want have everything now.
What's more, they hate reading.
They would rather watch films on the internet than reading books.
Secondly, using computers or tablets help to reduce amount of books in children's bag.
What's more, this situation helps protect environment by avoid deforestation.
On the other hand, books help student develop their attention span.
They have to focus on the topic more than 5 minutes.
Next, to find true information for homework is better to use books, because on the Inetrent students can find fake news.
To sum up, in the close future all schools and univeristy are able to use comuters or tablets instead of books.
