Nowadays, so many people are obsessed with exercise, or they think that this it is the most important thing to be fit and healthy, and although I think that it is necessary too, it is not as important as other things.
Firstly, whether you ask a doctor or a nutricionist, everyone is aware that sport is an essencial activity for our wellbeing, because it prevents us from coming down with illnesses, such as obesity, cardiac problems, it helps us to make faster recoveries, it strengthen us...
So it is indispensable to do exercise at least 30 minutes everyday But, however, a lot of people are wrong when they think that they only need to do that to be healthy, because there are other fundamental issues in our life that are necessary as well to be wholesome, for example, our social life, our mental health, the conditions and environment where we live....
A further point is that another super needded matter is our diet, because if you do not eat salubrious, exercise will not help you as much as it could.
In conclusion, sport is an indispensable activity in our life, but there are other things that are important too and we should not understimate them.
Health is an essential part of our life because it let us maintain each life-style.
A good health give us the opportunity to develop different activities and projects in a physic and mental way.
On the other hand, wealth is also important to maintain these life-style being that to keep good health people need to invest in healthy food, excersice even hobbies to preserve a good health, that is why both aspects of life are important.
Keeping healthy is not an easy challenge because of different aspects who are expensive nowadays.
But, health is not only about money or buy material things; health is also about being kind grateful charitable among others that means in simply words be a good human being.
Without a good health people can't maintain themselves to become wealth.
Besides being wealth is also important because let us keeping a good life quality, helping other people to overcome each difficult.
To sum up being health is a key element to be wealth because both aspects are important to human being develop to enhance a good life-style.
