Books and Technology In the world of today, more and more areas are taken over by thechnology.
Now many schools and universities are thinking of replacing books by computers and tablets.
Of course using a tablet instaed of a book has its advantages: Firstly, many students complain about that they have to carry so many heavy books.
If they used their laptop, with everything saved on there, they wouldn't have to carry loads of books with them.
