After while I had reached B1 and then B2.
Today I recieved evaluation C1 for first time.
It is proov that it has really improved my writing skills.
So I can honestly recommend this useful tool to you.
If you want to improve your writing skills from your home and you didn't have someone to help you, you could help yourself by this tool.
It is for free and it can be fun, too.
If nothing else you cold find out something interesting about yourself.
Writing improves not just your language skills but it helps your mind, too.
