In contemporary, many people in our society value to be rich very high.
However many researches imply that it is better to be healthy than to be rich if you have to choose one.
This essay discusses why to be healthy is more important than to be rich.
Firstly, many researches show that the people who are rich value their lives less than those are not rich.
Less confident causes many health problems.
For example, rich people who are less satisfied with their life consume proportionately more alcohol and they do less activity to stay fit.
There many diseases who are coming more for rich people than less affluent people.
Those diseases include heart infection and obesity.
Secondly, healthy is more important than wealth, because if you do not feel physically fit, but you have the money it would be very difficult to do each activity that you like.
If you are not able to things that you like because of health problems it can cause mental problems.
For example, you will estimate the value of life less and you can do things who can weakness further your health both physical and mental.
Another point that makes to be healthy more important to be rich is if you are healthy you are be able to become rich.
The reverse is in most cases not possible or easy.
There are many diseases that you cannot eradicate on your body, you to live those diseases for ever.
To summarize, to be healthy is very important.
If you are healthy you can do many activities who can make your life better and richer.
The converse is in many cases not possible
