Research recently has shown that Playing musical instruments can be considered as an effective phenomenal for people to feel more peaceful and improve their mental health.
As a way to manage people to achieve this goal, some schools have started teaching music to students and some of them have avoided donig that, due to the what scientists have found, music would help people to cencentrate much more.
When a musician start playing a piece, different oragans get involved to this activity and because it asks more compatibality, doing such a thing can help us to enhance our brain working.
