Speaking a foreign language still important nowadays?
I believe its more important than ever.
In the past, speaking a foreign language it was important, especially to get a good job.
However, today with the globalization, all the countries became more connected.
More connection between countries means that speaking another language is relevant to work, to study or for friendship.
I will explore the reasons in the essay below.
First of all, in the past speaking a foreign languague was related to work.
Usually people who spoken another languague worked in big companies overseas.
In theses days, even in small companies its required a second language.
For example, I worked in a familiar company in Brazil and it was necessary to speak and write and english to talk to the costumers.
Second, today with the internet, became easier to have contact with people around the world.
To talk to a foreigner you have to speak his languague.
In conclusion, its important to speak a foreign languague these days more than in the past.
