I believe the cultural exchange is one the most important things we can do in life.
I don\u00B4t see any disadvantage if you can afford it.
Maybe the only disadvantage is related to the money you should spend.
Studiying in another country could be expensive, specially if you do it in a great university or high school.
Apart form that, I see the exchange like an opportunity.
Being in touch with new cultures allow the student to grow as a person.
Learning new languagues could be one of the most important skills you could adquire.
At the end of the process you should be able to speak fluently other language.
Networking effect is an advantage of the experience too.
Knowing different people in different countries could be a great opportunity to increase your career.
As I mention in the beginning, in my view almost all are advantages if you finally decide to study abroad.
