Main problem that they might have, is about learning,understanding and speaking by a new language, for example of this,imagine a student who not know well the language of destination country that he want to go,it will be like a nightmare and he absolutely faces many problems in highschool or university and this problem might cause he cannot manage to understand his lesson.
Given to these fact, when we start to evaluate about the isssue, we discover the advantages of studing abroad outweigh the disadvantages and it depends on students' awareness of destination country.
Today studing abroard is regarded as a new opportunity to rise level of education which help people to culutural transmission.
