my experience with Write and Improve.
Write and Improve is a website where you can improve your writing through excercises.
these excercises will be checked for you and show where there is room for improvement.
a simple concept realy, but it has proven to be very successfull for me; ever since I've started using Write and Improve I've improved my writing a lot, without a great deal of effort.
I only wished it was a bit more organized, at first glance the website is a mess. but this is a small price to pay when using Write and Improve.
you can see your progress in graph on the right, this is a great feature.
sadly however, you can't scroll to previous results that don't fit in the graph. which comes as a rather significant annoyance.
in spite of these flaws, the website is a real life saver.
I'd recommend it to anyone hoping to improve their English.
