My reasons for learning English.
I am working very hard to enhance my English for many reasons.
Firstly, I have to speak and write English fluently for continuation of my study.
After my current study, I would like to follow a master study in the University.
One of the requirements that you have to meet to be admissible this master is an English level of at least C1 in all language aspects, reading, listening, writing and speaking.
Furthermore, I live a country that has an open economy.
In the Netherlands you have many international companies and if you look at each vocational job that is available they require high English level.
I have been using Write and Improve for a month.
I realize that writing English sentences every day makes my English abilities improve.
There are three reasons below.
Firstly, practising repeatedly and continuously is really important to improve something.
Secondly, you can focus on only writing English sentences without searching what you should write because the service offers a lot of topis to practice writing English.
The only thing you have to do is picking it up from those ones.
Lastly, there are many features there to encourage you study.
For instance. you can see your progress, feedbacks, topics lists on a dashboard if you log in the service.
Overall, writing English sentences on Writing and Improve is useful.
You should try it if you are struggling with writing in English, or searching the solution to improve your English abilities.
