I think that zoos are good place to learn about animals for people, especially young children.
There are two reasons below: Firstly, zoos offer opportunities to contact with many kind of animals.
I believe that spending time with animals has a positive impact on children's emotional development.
If they did not exist, children living in a big citiy such as Tokyo, New York, and so on might not be able to see and contact with any animals in their daily life, and it might give them to a negative impact.
Secondly, they have really important features such as not only an entertainment for people but also contribution of preservation of spicies by providing information about the lives of seveal kind of animals to some organizations.
We should tell children how zoos help our society through those activities.
For those reasons, zoos are good place for young children to learn about animals.
