The Future of Travel Currently, we have a lot of options to travel all around the world.
Higly-developed transportation systems such as airplane, ferry, and train makes it much easier to travel wherever we want to visit.
However, the world is dramatically changing in 2020 because of the COVID-19 pandemic.
Our activities are strictly being limited, and we have to stay home, work remotely without commuting.
I imagine that this situation will make our travel experiences change in the future.
For instance, it would be difficult to get a visa to travel or stay other countries because each government hesitate to approve it for preventing spreading the virus.
As a result, the value of traveling another country would increase.
Whereas, our trip to the major sightseeing spots could be more comfortable and enjoyable because of the decrease of a crowd of people.
Anyways, because of the coronavirus situation, the future of travel will be changed.
