I think there are things that are more important for our health.
Exercise is absolutely important, but it isn't the only way to keep our health.
Eating healthy food at regular time is important.
We should eat balanced meals.
We should also regulate its nutrition and volume.
Eating too much is bad for health.
It cause high blood glucose.
We have to eat determined value of calories divided to 6 times in a day to keep blood glucose value.
Sleeping well for 8 hours is also important for our health.
Good sleep make our bodies and mental health.
In order to sleep well, we shouldn't eat anything 2 hours before going to bed.
Avoiding stress in daily life is more important.
We need proper stress to keep our motivation in job or private lives, but excess stress may cause ill not only in our bodies but also our mental.
There are many things that are more important for our health besides exercise.
But most important thing is to continue these activities every day.
