Should people always tell the truth?
Or is it sometimes acceptable to tell a lie?
The first thing we need do is to ask ourselves: Is it a moral question or a social one?
To start, since our childhood we are told to never lie.
We heard: "lying is a bad thing, and you will hurt people if you do so."
Indeed we grew up and we believed that liars are terrible persons.
So, if we are responding this question from a moral point of views, I would say: we should never lie.
Nevertheless I believe it's more complicated than white or black.
Sometimes grey can help to avoid a lot of trouble.
In my views, lying from time to time is acceptable if the purpose is noble.
Sometimes a lie can be used to protect someone from being hurt and not the other way around.
Actually, let's take an example.
Someone cheats on someone else.
What is best thing to do ?
To tell the truth and destroy everything you built ?
To lie and to avoid to hurt the one you love ?
Of course, some poeple are just cowards, and lies beyond the truth.
But it's a very difficult question to judge.
Regardless this kind of interrogation, my opinion is: Hide the truth if the purpose is to avoid hurting someone.
Otherwise be bold and brave and speak you mind.
What is the Future of Travel ?
Will planes still be as numerous ?
Will trains be able to run faster ?
Will cars be flying?
Or conversely will we stop to travel ?
To begin with, all these questions still have no concrete answer.
Nevertheless if we look at the big picture we might find some responses.
These past few years, we have witness new political ideas.
People are more concerned than ever about ecology, and their well-being.
We know the traveling business brings a lot of pollution.
And we also know that the earth can't take it anymore.
So, to my views we must stop traveling the way we do.
We are killing our home, and it can't last any longer.
Indeed, discount fly compagnies have allowed many people to access plane travel.
We might see it as an improvement.
It is not.
I believe, twenty years from now car's ownership will drastically plunged.
Public transportation will rise and develop.
Finaly, I trust plane travel will be used for business trips only.
To conclude, the future of travel needs to be more responsible and eco-friendly.
It is our duty to be aware of what is coming.
