Teaching is an important job.
Teachers are people who contribute significantly to the development of students.
Some people think that it is beneficial for students to have the same teacher for many years, while others believe students will learn a lot more when they have different teachers.
In my opinion, it will be better when students can learn from a variety of teachers because each teacher has his/her talent and teaching method which directly affects the ability of students.
Having the same teacher year over year can make students feel bored.
When they are bored, students lose their interest in the lessons which affects their understanding and learning ability.
As a result, students can not absorb the new knowledge and might lose their interest in going to school.
Besides, if the teacher is responsible for all subjects over the years, their knowledge about the subject might not be well-researched because there a lot of things to learn.
Furthermore, lessons might not be well-prepared if the teacher teaches many subjects for many years.
On the other hand, students will benefit more from having different teachers each year.
Each teacher has their talent and will be professional in some specific fields.
Learning with these teachers helps students learn completely new things and they can be taught in some of the most understandable ways because teachers only need to focus on very narrow subjects and students.
In conclusion, changing teachers every year will benefit students since they can learn comprehensively from many different teachers over the years.
Eventually, students will develop and gain their knowledge to become good people.
