Studying abroad is a great experience for everyone.
However, as all choices that are made along life, there are advantages and disadvantages.
When studants are looking for a country to study, several times they are focusing on the cultural diversity or thinking about the beautiful places they can visit.
Obviously, this thought isn't wrong, but the truth is that they won't find just funny in the chose country.
A lot of problems can appear along the journy and the studands will have to handle with that without their parents, which can be the first time that it happen.
For example: the studants can not adapt with their new friends or they can find a big difficult with the language, because in the most cases, the studants go abroad thinking that can speak with natives, but when they have their first conversation, it doensn't work like used to work in their mind.
On the other hand, there are a lot of advantages that the new country can offer.
This experience can be the first time that the studants need to organize their freedom, because until this moment, they have always had their rotine planned by parents.
Furthermore, they will know new people from diferent places around the world and making conections with them will be a amazing experience for their lifes.
