To begin with, zoos had become very popular this last decades.
It allows people to learn about animals.
It is a popular place for family to spend some quality time.
However, some people trust it os wrong to keep animals in zoos.
In the first place I will tell you why zoos are important.
Then I will explain why I believe zoos are not good for animals.
Finaly I will give you my opinion about the future.
To star, zoos are not only created in order to entertain people.
As a matter of fact, most zoos helps to prevent extinction of endanger species.
For instance, only few black pandas still live widly and zoos have the duty to develop the panda's population.
Of course, humans are responsible for the animals missing but some zoos are trying to make it better.
Furthermore, zoos allows people to discover animals and to learn more about them.
In this way, I trust zoos are good places.
On the the other hand, I believe zoos are terrible for the well-fare animals.
I believe, it is wrong to keep a wild animal lock down into a forty meter square.
As an example, tigers need to run one hundred miles a day.
How is it possible in a zoo ?
Moreover, I think animals in zoos are unhappy and some might even suffer from depression.
To my views, zoos are a dangerous place for animals and their well-being.
Unfortunatly it had become an urge to develop some endanger population species and zoos only are able to do so.
In the future, I hope we would find a way to live peacefuly without destroying animal's homes.
