Over the last few years, I traveled a lot and I have been to many places.
However, my holiday in Sri Lanka remains my best memory ever.
In the first place, I will tell you where I have been and what I saw.
In the second place, I will explain you why it was the best holiday I ever had.
To begin with, it was the first time I ever visited Asia.
