Video games are widespread among children.
Playing video games might be advantageous to them.
Nevertheless, it will bring some drawbacks if parents cannot control how their children play video games.
This essay will analyze the advantages and disadvantages when children play video games.
On the one hand, playing video games can be beneficial.
Firstly, it helps children relax after hours of studying.
When they have time to rejuvenate, children will have more energy to go back to their studies.
Secondly, while playing games, children can learn some new skills such as problem-solving, time management, and teamwork (if they play games together), which are necessary for themselves later in life.
Challenges in video games force children to think, to use their minds to find solutions, and to help each other for the final target.
These are some benefits when children play video games.
On the other hand, it might be harmful if children play games too much.
Hours of looking at the screen will damage their eyes, which leads to many negative effects in children's life.
They will not learn effectively and fully develop with an unhealthy eyes.
Also, playing games too much make children tired.
From that, they will be less active and lose their interests in other kinds of activities such as running and playing outdoors.
These are the reasons why parents should monitor and limit the time of playing video games of their children.
In conclusion, playing video games is a double-edged sword.
Although it contributes positively to the development of children, there are still many drawbacks.
Parents should be aware of these advantages and disadvantages to help their children control the use of video games.
To keep chlidren occupied by usefull activities is usually a great challenge for parents.
in the past, reading a book or watching television were enough for enjoying children but now it's very diffuclt to satisfay them.
The video games are obviously the favourite occupation that children prefer in this century. but why?
In my modest opinion, it's due for the frame of games: it's occure them all the things that they need like advertisments, connectionwith other freinds or sel esteem feeling.
Many parents consiousless about the danger that video games represent.
It's proved that using video games for a long time leed children for a dangerous type of psychological disease like shkisofrenia.
In my case I believe stongly that video games are vry dangerous and I will do evreything in my ability to avoid my children to use it.
unstead of that, I will certaily encourage them to be freind with book and magazine.
To summarize my opinion, I will encourage my children to be creative.
