I believe that living longer is better because it is a signe of well lived life and a longer service for other people.
I believe in the old adage that says "to live better you need to hide."
People who live a good live are generally those who have choosen to do everything moderately.
For example, having good health habits such as eating moderately and not allowing excess alcohol might lengthen the live.
Although the lenght of one's life can be determined by many things, one should definitely avoid degerous activities.
Some people for instance choose to dry very carlessly or very fastly on road just to show to the world how smart they are.
This behaviour sometime, can lead to a sudden death.
Moreover, living an intense life doesn't always mean living well or being helpfull to other peoples.
For example, mother Theresa of India had lived a long life but had been of a tremendous help for many people in the world.
This means that life does not necesseraly need to be intense to be meaningful.
Many have lived a long an enjoyable life without being famous or known by everyone at every side of the globe.
This said, I prefer a longer and smooth live instead of a shord life full of exessive behaviours.
To conclude, we do not all determine the lengh of our life.
And we can only try to bring the best out of the time we have existed.
I started using Write and Improve few days ago and I am really excited about it.
Firstly, write and improve is a program on the internet which helps you improve your English writing.
There are many different topics you can choose and write about it.
The program is capable to correct your text and show you what level of English it was.
After that you can correct the essay and it will show you your progress.
But how does it correct your text exactly?
The program shows you all mistakes in spelling and grammar which is common in most of the writing programs.
What's more Write and Improve can check your whole sentences too.
On the other hand there are some things missing in this program which I would use.
These are for instance suggestions how to improve or correct your sencence and most importantly the explanation of your exact level of English and how to improve it when you correct everything and have no mistakes left.
Furthermore in Write and Improve there were some mistakes too.
I used one common English phrase and this program corrected me.
All things considered I would recommend Write and Improve for all students who want to learn how to write in English.
Anyway there is still many space to upgrade this helpful tool for students.
