Sport is very important exercice for our health.
Doing exercises especially in the morning has a huge benefit for our moral as well as mood spirit.
Personally, I prefer doing jogging.
This old sport is easy and helpful.
We can practice it either in cities or in the gardens.
As I live near the sweet beaches, what I like so much is obviously swimming as well as surfing; these two sports have many advantages and had a numerous good effect on our health.
We can practice them regularly and easily either during spring or summer.
Besides Sport, I continue to believe that there are many other activities that we can practice like Yuga and meditation.
These two Asiatic disciplines are widely practiced not only in India but also in other countries around the world.
To summarize my opinion, I\u2019m convinced that the sport is the main activity that having a good and deep impact for our health and consequently for our heart.
