In summary I think that obigatory work for high scholls is a good thing if it has not need too much time and you still have a choise what kind of work you would like to do.
In fact, video games are very popular nowadays with children.
Recently, technology has made it possible for children to have fun at the comfort of their homes compared to the times when children very often need to be taken outdoors to have entertainment, and that's very good.
However, there are indeed some positive and negative effects.
the positive effects of video games on children is that children can have more fun at home - playing and expressing themselves through games.
In addition, parents of children will have the chance to do home activities while children are busy with playing video games.
In spite of that, video games contents can be very aggressive nowadays, and not appropriate with young children who are under 18 years old. Because, this will pose negative impact on the child's personality, because they are in a age that isn't allowed to view violent or aggressive content even when they are on the Internet.
Although parents can still have control on what their children are viewing whether on Televsion or the Internet or a video game.
And apparently, computer devices now have parental control settings, where partents can restrict or trace their chirdren's activity online.
With the appearace of some video games that contain violent scenes, children are becoming more violent-loving.
And that what explains the violence among school children recently such as the violence we see in some shooting and murder games, although these games are targeted at teenagers and adults.
But, young children are increasingly wanting to play such games, because it is spread among their older siblings.
I think, parents need to be aware of the good types of video games to buy for their chilrdren and make sure these games do not contain violence or targeted at the age of their chilrdren.
