In my opinion, the better choice for these students is to move away and live on their own while they are attending school.
Of course, this is the most difficult choice because it is necessary for these students to work and get their own salary.
With a job, they have less time for their other activities like working their exercises, having fun with their friends or cooking.
Therefore, with this experience, they can becoming more independant and responsible.
They can also gain autonomy.
However, live at home with their family is also a good choice.
They are less lonely, they have always a contact with their family and they feel better.
Moreover, one of the most advantage of this situation that these students spend less money.
However, it is more easy for them to have a party in their flat that their parent's home.
Personally, I have lived the both experiences and I preferred when I was alone, in my own flat.
