On my university there are many students who live in student house.
But, there are also students who have prefered for different reasons to stay their parents home.
In my openion, it is better that students live in a student house for different reasons.
In this essay I will entail why I believe that student house is better choice that staying with your parents.
Firstly, living on your own is better than living with your parents on your university time, because students who live alone develop skills that they needfor their foreseeable future.
Living alone means that your have to cook yourself.
Furthermore, living alone makes you notified what it means to live alone.
You are also learning taking properly decisions, because are aware of your responsibilit.
Therefore, you are pondering before making paramounts decisions.
However, there are many aspects who impede students to live alone in their students.
The livelihood is in many Western-countries increasing considerably.
Therefore, many students can afford to live in a student house.
Furthermore, many universities are established in cities where house supply is dramatically low.
As a ramification, many students can find student house and are coerced to stay with their parents.
