The main question is whether is it sometimes better to say a lie than the truth.
I believe that telling the truth can not bad at all, as I said before.
Nevertheless the truth is that you can hurt someone with the truth or cause some problems in relationships etc.
For instance if someone asks you whether he\u2019s fat you might lie to him because you don\u2019t want to hurt him.
There is also the option not telling anything which could be the best decision in many situations.
I thing that it is allways better than a lie because the lie is bad in substance.
To put it another way if you don\u2019t want to answer the question with a lie you should probably not tell anything.
All things considered I thing that in situiations where you shouldn\u2019t tell the truth you ought to not answer.
If it is not possible, than you might lie but only because of a good purpouse.
