These last years and especially this year with the Coronavirus pandemic, we saw the following problem: A majority of medical doctors want to work in cities where they will make a lot of money while there are not enough doctors in many rural areas.
Thus one wonders what are the reasons for this problem ?
Firstly, a majority of medical doctors want to work in cities because they have their friends near them and they can doing a lot of activities.
In brief, the major advantage is the human contact.
Secondly, the wages are more attractive in cities thant in rural areas.
So now we have identfied the reasons of this problem, what could we do ?
Firstly, we could increase the salary for medical doctors who accept to work in rural areas.
We could also regroup all medical doctors who work in rural areas on a same competitiveness hub.
