There is no doubt that these days Writing&Improving website becoming very popular.
However, the quetion: Is this website realy help the students to improve their writing or not?.
It is considered one of the most controversial issues today.
In this essay , I am going to examine this phenomenon from the both viewpoints.
On one side of this argument ther people who are argue that the considerable benefits outwigh the disadvantages.
To illustrate ,the main reason for believing this is writing & improving website has a lot of tools which are perfect to help students to write from beginning because there are four level for writing first level is for beginner and then to intermediate and finally for advanced and business.
The first level , which is for beginner, include some questions which make the students thinking about the answer and write it in easy way.
Moreover, this website has some parts to preper for IELTS test .
On the second point of this argument some people argue that the website is profitable, and it provides some amounts from writing and after that you have to pay to complate your proggress in writing.
Fourthermore, they request high fee to letthe learner to improve his or her writing .
As we have seen, There are no one easy answer to this quetion.
On balance, however, I tend to believe that this website is so good to help all students to improve their writing skills.
The first aspect to point out is all around the world, people are spending more and more time doing sedentary activities.
During their leisure time, people like to sit on sofas, watching TV, playing games or just socializing with others.
The problem is that many children take their parents example and that can give them diseases.
One solution for this problem is to force kids to do sports activities.
To begin with, an extremely important place where you understand aspects about life and gain knowledge to help in materializing your future is school.
But school should have provide more physical activities for kids to take part in.
For instance, children spend on average six hours in school every day while students can stay at school for eight hours.
That is a lot of time just to sit on a chair and listen to someone.
Children are getting bored as the time pass and they do not pay attention anymore at what the teacher is saying.
Secondly, not only are physical activities good to increase attention, but also they reduce high cholesterol, high blood presure, obesity and feelings of depression and anxiety.
For example, one of my acquaintances had problems with anxiety and his therapist recommended him to do exercises and take walks.
That worked for him and now he is really fond of sports activities.
Because those activities made him one of the happiest people I have ever know.
On the other hand, there are kids who feel uncomfortable when they are doing exrcises in front of the other children.
Some are often rude and make fun of other's bodies and that can cause self-esteem problems.
However, I believe that the results of doing exercises are worth it.
To conclude, phyisical activities are a necessity in order to feel good, be healthy and look good.
More people should do sport because is wholesome and they will have many advantages after doing that.
Some high schools have a requirement that students must complete a certain amount of volunteer work in order to graduate.
I found this requirement absolutely appropriate, because it highlights a problem which most of the times is too much underestimated: that one of social activism.
We are habits to do things in order to receive something back, but sometimes things must be done just because they are right.
In a society which wants to define itself civil people must help the next one without asking for something back.
Helping just to help, without any other purpose, is a wonderful way to make that the personal cultural luggage of everyone grows up.
Volunteer work offers the possibility to meet people with different experiences, perhaps coming from other countries or from families with difficult conditions, or to care about animal which had unluckely been adopted by the wrong person.
It offer also the possibility to understand different way of living and to take conscience of the problems which the community has.
It is possible making a volunteer work cleaning seasides from plastic or organizing benefical events to collect money for the associations located in the territory.
There are several possibilities to do something good for the community and this is a very relevant point, because everyone can help according to their attitudes.
Volunteer work also allows to learn to be less selfish, which is not so obvious in our days, and that none nor nothing have to be left behind.
I have been learning English for more than 20 years but I have never seen any website for learning English writing which has a feature as good as 'Write and Improve' before.
With this website, you can practise writing anywhere if you have a mobile phone or a tablet.
There are tons of assay topics devided in 3 different levels that students can choose on their own.
After finishing writing, this website provides the ability of text checking, therefore, the writings are evaluated and are given a feedback in only a few seconds.
If the students have corrected their writing, the graph will show the improvement compared with the previous one.
However, there are some problems I found while I was using this website.
First, the fonts are too small and the background colour is too bright.
Second, I would suggest that the feedback should be more specific to each writing errors because it is hard to find what the writers do wrong by theirselves without direct hints.
After all, I would like to recommend this website to you, readers.
You cannot find any other websites which give you the great opportunity to improve your English without any fee.
I believe that this website will gradually be better and become a promising way to learn writing.
