Ther is no doubt that these days Video games becoming very popular between cildren.
However, the question: is it useful for children?
It is considered one of the most controversial issues today.
In this essay , I am going to examine this phenomenon from both viewpoints.
On one side of the argument there are people who argue that the benefits considerable outwigh the disadvantage for video games.
Themain reason for believing this is video games assist children to learn new skills and focus on achieve the goal from the games at the end.
Addationally, video games create competition between children to do the best and win.
On the other hand from the argument, thereare people whobelie that video games are not benefit and it make negative effect on the children.
To illustrate, children spend long time play without stopping that is not healthy for them .
Aswe have seen, there is no one easy answer to this question.
On balance, however, I tend to believe video games is good choice for entertainment for children, but must parents be careful about their children to be aware about what they play.
