Sometimes telling truth it is the collar of the surviving from the conflicting, worthless, aurelaible because the vast mojority of people hate liar person.
lying on people means losing confidance no body accept that, moreover most of them ignore liars people, the resone is the consequences that was copming after believe them or even the problems from their speech.
We always see liar person spreading rumores and trying to make problem with others.
deception and laying they are common humam behaviors.
There are many researchs prove that.
Psychologists have utilized research on body launguge and deception to helps members of law enforcement distinguish between the truth and lies, and results providing the signs of liar people are: 1- being vague: If the speaker seems to intentionally leave out important details, it might be because they are lying 2- vocal uncertainly: If the person seems unsure or insecure, they are more likelu to perceived as lying 3- indiffirence: shrugging, lack of experssion and a bored posture can be signs of lying 4- overthinking: if the person seems to be thinking too hard to fill in the details of the story. it might because they are deceiving you.
The conclusion here while body launguge may be helpful, it is important to pay attention on the right signs .
