On, balance, howeever, I tend to beleive that studying music is very interesting if the students want that, so I think studying music good to be elective class for students who interest to learn it.
The experience of studying abroad at young ages is the advantage.
Recently, studying abroad is not an uncommon experience for ordinary people.
Some parents are eager to let their children go to another country to study language and culture in that country.
On the other hand, it is said that studying abroad with no purpose is meaningless.
In my opinion, it is a useful experience for young people to go to another country and learn about their culture.
It allowed them the opportunity to see the world from another perspective.
People who live in another country should learn about language and culture, which usually is not familiar to them.
It might be hard to understand all of them.
However, they can achieve another perspective by touching new thought and culture, and that is a strong advantage to live.
If they can not go familiar with another culture, the experience of studying abroad might be worst memory.
It is not easy to have friends and a reliable person casually in a foreign country.
The sense of failure and non-fruitful memory frustrated them after returning home.
Anyway, studying abroad can be a positive challenge for young people.
If you can get such experience at young ages, you have the advantage already.
The best teacher in life is their own experience.
