Medicine is an ardous work to do because doctors not only have to spent many hours on guard but also they have to study hard to become a good proffesional.
That is the reason why a lot of doctors want to work in a good hospital in cities instead of rural areas.
This problematic causes that there are no enough doctors there.
Besides of that, lack of doctors in rural areas is because those doctors who have to go there; they have to leave their family or friends and the life cost is difficult because there are no facilities that a city provides.
