What I most like about Write and Improve is the feedback.
In a few minutes it is possible to know what aspects are necessary to improve and the main mistakes that were made, including grammar and vocabulary.
On the other hand, it is very hard to know what is the mistake when appear only a sentence in different color and there are not suggestions to make the sentence better.
I would love if the program could show me some options to improve my sentences.
To sum up, I definitely recommend this tool for my classmates.
It is an easy and interesting way to improve English writing any time you want without worring about judgment.
This report about experience with Write and Improve in use for practicing and improving my English writing.
