There are many topic that you can choose to practice to write English.
Those topics are about all thing and from beginers to advanced levels.
The second thing I like this course is online course.
That means you can pratice writing English at any time and any where.
The third is progess report that help me to know how my writing is improve or not after finishing each work.
On the other hand, I disliked how Write and Improve course correct my writting.
It rivesed and commented my sentences in general but did not give me suggeted or replaced sentences.
In general, Write and Improve is intersting website to practise and improve your English and I am so sure to recommend it my classmates to try it.
