Improvements are proved Have you ever wanted to improve your writing skill, but you didn't know where to start?
If this seems familiar to you, Write and Improve might be the perfect tool for you to step up your writing skill and to impress others with your writing talent.
I recently discoverd their site, which is not only easy accessible but also completly free to use.
How does this tool work and, more importantly, is it worth trying?
The website, provided with a clear and neat interface, consists of different workbooks with writing excercises.
Whatever level of English you have, there will be an appropiate workbook task for you.
You can hand in your writing and you will receive immediately detailed feedback.
Moreover, there is a timer function and a graph to track your writing progress.
Hence, in my opinon, this tool is really beneficial to your language skills.
The immediate checks make you more aware of the mistakes you make.
In adittion, the site provides you with advice on how to improve.
To me, this tool was indeed really helpfull for preparing for my camebridge exam.
However, it should be noted that the website doesn't mark all your spelling mistakes nor gramatical errors.
Therefore, it would be wise to also ask a teacher to check your work, instead of just relying on the tool.
Likewise, sometimes they give unclear feedback, which make it difficult to improve even more.
Despite the tool not always working properly, I would still recommend it to anyone who wants to improve their writing skill.
To practice is the key to any skill and Write and Improve creates a great only learning environment for doing so.
So, why don't you give it a go?
