There are plenty of useful online resources for English learners.
Everything can be found online, from improving vocabulary to practising grammar, from interactive worksheet to printable worksheet.
Sometimes I find it too overwhelming and hard to focus on only one website.
Besides, one website can't satisfy what I am looking for.
However, when it comes to writing part "Write and Improve" is the one and only tool for me.
Why is it so great?
You can choose tasks according to your level.
Once you write enough words for each task, your worksheet will be checked, and score will be informed instantly.
Moreover, you can see the feedback, for instance, what mistakes have you made, what words are misspelled.
Then you have chances to change and improve your writing to reach a better level.
I don't find it difficult to use this tool.
It has a clear lay out.
Easy to understand and follow.
Other than that, you can be awarded when you accomplish some tasks, which encourage you to continue practising.
It seems to me that I found the right and perfect tool for my writing skill.
Whoever is still trying to upgrade your writing, either for fun or for a test. Write and Improve is the best tool that you shouldn't miss out.
