Nowadays is becoming more and more popular to do exercises.
Many studies have shown that a reasonable amount of exercise can improve your healthy, so more and more people has started to do them.
I had a class discussion on the importance of exercise yesterday afternoon.
There were a lot of different opinions about this topic especially how to do them and if they were the most important thing in the life.
This is always a tricky problem, because like everything in the life the important thing is the balance.
If you spend the whole day to do exercises you will not have time for your family, for your girlfriend or boyfriend and for your friends.
In fact when you only dedicate your time in the gym or in your home doing exercise probably you always lost something in terms of friendship or love.
On the other hand if you don't dedicate a bit of your time for exercises you damage your helathy in particular when you become older.
For these reasons, as I said before, the secret in this tricky problem is the balance, so in other you have to take time for yourself but also for your affects.
