Nowadays more and more strudents decide to study in another country for a certain time.
It is becoming a sort of fashion but sometime the students have strong reasons to do it.
Studying abroad can have both advantages and disadvantages.
The advantages can be both for your carrear and for you culture.
A positive aspect when you go in a foreign country is that you can learn another language, which can be useful in terms of carrear when you find a job.
Another positive aspect is the opportunity to find out other cultures and traditions that can improve yourself like a person.
The disadvantages are due to be away from your family and if you are very young can be a very difficult thing to put up with.
However in my opinion the advantages are more than the disadvantages because an experience like this can help you to grow faster and to face life in the best way.
