Except the affluent countries like US,students in poor countries wish to study abroad.
They believe that their education system is much more higher than theirs.
Lagging behind the western countries,most of students in Asian countries are trying to go abroad and study in it.
Not only the undergraduates but also the gratuates go abroad to get a job with high salary. Because they know that their government is not able to create a special post for them.
But some students do not want to go abroad as they are not accustomed to their culture and something like that.
From my point of view,I want to study abroad and serve for my country.
As you know,studying abroad is not easy,you will experience culture shock certainly.
You have to habituate to their food,culture and weather.
Worse than that,you might get bullied .
To the best of my knowledge,it has been said that some western people discriminate against Asian people on the grounds of the race or ethnicity.
On the other hand,there are a lot of advantages studying abroad.
As you have to learn their language, you will become a bilingual.
And you get to know their culture and lifestyle.
You begin to know the difference between your country and their country.
You will get a ton of knowledge since you can see and learn many different things from them.
And with that knowledge, you can serve and strive for your native country's development.
