English is an international language.
Many people around the world speak English as a first or second language.
It is vital to have a command of this language for communication with other nationalities.
International companies use this language to make trade agreements with other countries.
Therefore, it is an advantage that your resume can speak different languages.
Besides, English students have another goal in learning, taking an international test such as Toefl or IELTS.
International certification is essential for entering college or starting studies abroad, it is one of requirements.
Another exciting aspect is that learning provides a high understanding of the world.
Language is not separate from culture; on the contrary, it is a cultural element.
You begin to understand the world from a different perspective.
In the English view, you immerse new social rules, new concepts and thoughts.
