Write and Improve website is an incredible website for practising writing in English for English learners.
Since I've started to write on this website, I've found that my English writing has improved tremendously.
Practising writing often on this website, bringing back forgotten words to my memory.
I've started to pay more attention to 'noun', 'adjective', 'adverb' and a structure of every sentence more now.
I'm still making mistakes but it's not that bad as before.
I like the awards system and the calendar of how often I write very much.
Those awards keep me going and encouraging me to do more practice.
To be able to see my writing level up or down immediately is also making me want to do better and better each time.
I'm really impressed with the instant feedback too.
I'm not a patient person so to be able to see the constant feedback is remarkable.
There is one thing that I don't like though.
I think the workbooks for beginner level is not a lot.
There should be triple of what they have at the moment.
I would recommend this website to people I like because it thinks this website can help them with their English writing.
