There is no doubt that volunteer work has a value for our lifes and that is why I agree with the statament.
In my opinion, volunteer work is a valid requirement for studants.
Volunteer work is a first step to devolep empathy and responsability.
In this essay I will explore the reasons.
Firstly, volunteer work is a win-win situation.
That means is a mutual benefit.
For the students which develop soft skills, empathy and responsability and for those who receive.
Secondly, many students who start a volunteer work at high schools brings the experience for the rest of their lifes.
As an example, during my high school I did a volunteer work with orphans.
This experience changed my life and even after I graduated I continued to visit them.
Also, I did some campaigns for donation which helped to buy food and many other things they need.
Thus, volunteer work can be a changing in our lifes and a mutual benefit.
I prefer having new teachers each year.
Having new teachers each year can have many benefits for students.
One of the benefits is reducing the likelihood of the teacher having favourite students and make other students feel left out because of this bias.
No matter how much ethical a teacher might think he or she has, some of those teachers might fall into this trap without having realized they are having them.
Each teacher has a different set of skills she or he uses to teach students.
This mean, students will be able to compare and perhaps learn what skills that enhance their ability to study the most.
Being adapting to a new teacher every year will give students another proficient skill to adapt to changes outside of school.
They can learn to get on with new people and manage to establish the relationship easier when they have some sort of those skills beforehand.
Getting to know a new teacher can be an exciting experience.
It can stimulate the learning curve of students to the better.
Students are young people, and at their age, they always looking for something new and thrilling.
They might want to go to school more because of this reason, thus, will not see school as boring as much as before.
Therefore, I encourage all school to have new teachers each year.
