In my opinion, Health is of way more priority rather than wealth.
There are absolutely no disadvantages of having excellent health.
For example, if we are very rich but our health is not impressive then we will probably die soon and our wealth will be of no use.
Could it save our health?
It could not!
On the other hand, if we have marvelous health but don't have that much money, we can still live a long life.
If we are not healthy, we cannot even enjoy our life properly, because it wil be so small that we wont be able to store precious moments of our family and friends.
We will then realise the real meaning of 'Health is wealth'.
It will come in our mind that our wealth was of no use and coudn't even save us from death.
Thus, it is proved that health should be on a higher pedestal than our wealth because wealth is of little use but health is very precious.
