You can't deny that rainy season is very helpful to the agriculture .
The luxuriant vegetation are likely to grow with the help of rain.
The verdant surroundings make everyone feel peaceful when they take a look at it.
On the other hand,some areas are flooded because of the heavy rain.
And, of course, mud is the most disgusting thing in this season.
Moreover, there may be some difficulties in transportation.
