Today I am going to review about a English website called Write and Improve.
This website is published by Cambridge and most of the students don't know how good this website is.
In this website there are many levels for your writing skills so you choose your writing skill.
Also there are many essays, letters, reports and review in one level.
So you choosing what you like.
The writing levels are beginner, Intermediate, Advanced, Business and Just for fun.
Also there are IELTS General Training.
You can save your writing by making Cambridge account.
This website also check out writing skill and the website show our skill with paragraph.
In paragraph there are many levels.
Those levels were same as Cambridge English.
Like A1, A2, B1 and etc.
Also they check our writing essays, letters and etc.
If there are mistakes they show with red line and they are also words entered in every essay s and others.
If you are not in the word entered in essays you can't submit your essay and the website won't check too.
I used this website for 4 months and my writing skills level were improved.
In first essay, I got A2 level and after 4 months my level were go to B2.
I think this website is for students writing skill.
I recommend this website for every students.
I hope this website helpful to every students.
Bye.
First of all, I think that the exercise is not only important for our physical health but also contributes to have a better quality of life, due to when we work out we have more energy for our daily activities, we feel more relaxed and reduce our stress levels.
However there are other things that we can considered as important as exercise even there are others that we considered more important.
One instance of this could be, learning a new language, which could represent an opportunity to develop a new skill, have more knowledge and be able to communicate with other people in our work and personal life, also we often considered imprescindible to learn a new language in order to visit other countries, meet new people, know other cultures and traditions, besides it means an opportunity to enjoy a wonderful trip, which is one of my personal goals.
Apart from that, I think my studies are really important for us as students and sometimes we dedicate more time to study for tests than the exercise; owing to, what we learned during our years in university would be essential so as to have a successful future career.
In addition, I would say that dedicate time to our family is also more important than exercise, so in order to drive this home, I think not only our families are our foundation and our support when we are feeling down, but also they are who can we share our achievements and hapinnes with.
Finally, I would say that, indeed there are other things that have more priority over exercise but that doesn't mean that we are carelessly in that aspect, it just mean that we would often make decisions about what to do with our time and our lives according to our priorities and what we want to achieve in the long term.
