Today I choose the topic an opinion essay Health or wealth.
In my opinion everybody says that the health is more important than wealth, of course.
But the reality is different.
There is the compulsory health insurance in Europe.
When we are childern the compulsory health insurance is payed by the Czech republic, when we are 18 years old we have to pay ourselves.
We have the health care in each moment in the system of the insurance.
If anyone has no job he has to be in the evidence of unemployed.
He gets a dose each month and the compulsory payments are payed by the Czech republic.
The second situation is in USA.
It is a opposite side.
The health care is not for everybody.
I can pay for the health insurace but I do not have to pay it.
If I am ill and I have to go to the doctor I have to pay for all injections and pills.
The future of Travel Nowadays we are facing a new era in which the coronavirus has brought up changes in our ways to do the things and one of them is the way we travel.
So I think travel will be different in the future, starting with the quantity of people allowed to enter to some places such as museums, stadiums and parks.
Besides, it will likely that people prefere to go to close places rather than further countries.
On the top of that I believe that the technology and the artifitial intelligence are going to play an important role in traveling, one instance of this could be that now thanks to them there are going to be offered simulations of different travels to different countries in which people will be able to experiment a trip hence they will have the opportunity to take a better decision of where places to visit.
Apart from that, I think the way we transport and travel is going to change in the future, in view of technology has advanced too much I think there will be other kinds of airplanes and cars, which also are going to be cheaper and more accesible.
On the other hand, I think there are many ways of traveling which might still be the same in the future, such as the routes of travels, these routes wouldn't change because they have been determined taking into account the preservation of the touristic places.
In addition, I think travelers are going to still make reservations in hotels or hostel before to arrive to another country and people still would prefer to eat out in the future rather than stay at home and cook.
