In history of human life, we saw in rich class parents, sent children to boarding school, but most of them stayed at home, because they have not enough money to send children to boarding school.
But why parents send children to boarding, because they want their children learn how to live independently.
Students who go to university to continue their education, move away from their families, and live in independently, have advantages and disadvantages.
Most important results are: they learn how to deal with problems and solve them alone, they face problems that have not encountered before and are forced to a find a solution to them, and this is very useful for their future.
of course, every student could not live on their own.
Another important case is they learn how to deal with other people.
Conclusion: life students on their own is important for future life, they learn how to deal problems and deal with other people.
Therefor I suggest every student if they could live on their own.
What is the best office to work in?
From parents, friends, films, books or other sources I know two generall types of offices.
The first one is when everyone is sitting in the same room and can comunicate without e-mails or phones, but just by shouting or going to the neigbour.
Such officec are usefull for worker who have a group-project, because they need to exchange permanetly in order to stay on the same level.
But in my opinion the socond offices designe is better.
Here everyone or two persons together have their own room.
At first they can create their rooms like they want in order to have a suitable atmosphere.
Another positive point about wirking alone is that you are not distracted by other people.
I knew from school that working with a lot of people simultaneously is very difficult, because people speak about every topic except the task to be done.
In summery I think that working in the same building, so you can spend your lunchenon with colegue, is good, but sharing a big office with 10 people is not efficient for your work.
Nowadays a lot of young adults, teenagers and school children are struggling with obesitas symptoms.
This is because most of them are sitting inside for the whole day and do not enough sport activities.
Because of this, it can be questioned if it is appropriate to force all mentioned young people to do exercise activities at least three times a week.
The first advantage for forcing students to excersise three times a week is to make sure that they are not behind their laptops or tablets on these moments.
When teenagers are the whole day inside behind their screens, they do not move enough.
As a result, the children develop not as much motorical movements as they should do for their personal development.
The second advantage is that children improve their unhealthy lifestyle.
Since students eat to much unhealty food and exercises too little, a lot of teenagers are almost diabetic patients or they show more often obesitas symptoms than approximatly thirty years ago.
A disadvantage for forcing students is that not all people have the ability to pay contribution, because they do not earn enough money or to go for a sport activity that is further away because their parents do not have a car.
For those poor families, the goverment has to pay for the sport lessons of these student if the state wants to force them to go.
In summary, it is a good idea to force students to exercise more often so that young people can improve their lifestyles.
For poor families is a gift from the goverment neccessary and after that, also children from those families are able to excercise more often.
We,humans have to work for a living.
We need food to be alive and we need shelter to live comfortably.
Consequently, we need money to some extent.
However, money can't solve any problem; it can't buy us happiness.
In order to live peacefully,health plays a vital role in our daily life.
It seems to me that health is more important than wealth.
Do you ever ask yourself if you live to work or work to live?
For me,I work to live.
Being healthy is a blessing:you can do anything you want and go anywhere you want.
In other words, you can't do whatever you would like to if you are not good in health.
For example,supposing you are ill,you can't go to school or work.
You would have to stay at home until you are well.
Besides, your mother would go out of her way and make time to take care of you.
There would be nothing good for you.
That's why you have to stay healthy physically and mentally.
It is essential to not forget that you are enough.
We don't need to try to be wealthy like others.
I am not saying that being wealthy is not good at all.
As I mentioned above, we need money to live properly.
I mean that we should not work desperately without taking good care of health,which lead to disorder.
In fact,we will not able to make money if we are unhealthy.
To sum up,I strongly believe the idea that " healthy is a wealthy " .
For the reasons I mentioned above, I personally believe that health is definitely important than wealth.
