There are a variety of activities which require high school students to complete before entering either a university or working live.
One of them is voluteer work, in my opinion this type of work is genuinely suitable for high school students.
There are a lot of reasons for joining volunteer work.
For instance, they can learn how to deal with difficult situation once they enter the real working world and they can find their own passion throughout their volunteer work.
Volunteer work is the right way for high school students to practise their skills outside the classroom.
They are able to witness the work system in each job ,moreover they can learn how to handle and be prepared for a difficulty which they will encounter later once they have a full-time job.
Another good reason for being a part of volunteer work is students are able to search for a job that suits their abilities and personalities.
They will try out from volunteer work whether they like to persue that career or completely change to different career paths.
In conclusion, high school students should be introduced to volunteer work, so they will be able to cope with any obstables that will be thrown to them.
And also they wil be able to search and select the right job for their future.
