As you know,I am the hard-core fan of South Korean boy band named BTS.
I've always wanted to attend their concert.
But I never had a chance to go. Because their concert tickets are too expensive for a student like me to buy.
But you know, my grandfather had given me pocket money before they announced the concert date.
With that pocket money, I bought the ticket.
Some might think that it is unreasonable spending such an amount of money on a concert ticket.
