Novemeber 2, 2020 My Dear Town Council: The freedom of free exercise is guaranteed to every American citizen by the First Amendment of the Constitution.
However, this freedom is at odds with a recently proposed idea to ban mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants.
I disagree with the banning of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants.
Firstly, all citizens are guaranteed the freedom of free exercise.
So, the Town Council cannot ban the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants unless people are doing something against the law.
So, the Town Council cannot impliment this ban because it goes againts the First Amendment.
This a major reason why I disagree with banning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants.
In addition, mobile phones make it easier for people to pay for items, food, and public transport.
If the Town Council impliment this ban, then people would have to carry lots of coins and paper currency whenever they want to buy something at a shop or when they are eating at an restaurant.
This means that if this ban is caried out, it would make people's life much harder.
This another reason why is disagree with this proposed ban.
All in all, I disagree with this proposed ban both because it is unconstitutional, and that its makes people's life harder.
I hope that the Town Council rethink and not impliment this ban after reading this letter.
Yours sincerly, Daniel
Some people think that it is a good idea for people not to lie, while other say it is acceptable not to speak truth.
However, I believe that every individual should try to speak the truth always because it would help people to build a connection of trust between each other, I think it is acceptable to speak lie when it don not hurt other people.
On the one hand, some think that it is necessary to always speak the truth.
This is because people can build a strong relation between each other by speaking the truth always and this type of connections mostly does not break.
For instance, a 2015 report by UK government found that the pupils aged between 5-12 shares strong bond other children than young and old people because children's does not lie as young people do.
So I agree it is very important to try not to lie to others, especially to loved ones.
Other people would say that sometimes, it is okay to speak lie rather than truth.
One reason for this is that some situation where truth hurts and separate the people in some situations so it is acceptable to lie.
For example, according to extensive research, couple sometime lie to save their marriage which according to me is also acceptable.
To conclude, although views differ whether it is okay for people to lie sometimes, I would argue every individual must try to speak the truth first which allow people to share healthy bond.
