Some people think that it is necessary to learn a foreign language skills as it was earlier, while others say it is of no benefit nowdays .
I believe that it is more important these days to have other languages becuase it provides an opportunity to make new friends and help to get good pay skill job.
One reason for this is that, nowdays, people travel cross borders to experience new cultures.
Knowing language of other countries help people to fill a communication gap so that people can interact with each other freely and become friends.
For instance, a survey by France government found that people who know foreign langauge make new friends easily and enjoies the culute at bestof that country as compared to people who know native language.
Therefore, I think foreign language are more important and should be taught from middle schools.
Another reason why i think that it is of so much benefit because language allow people to do business between countries People can enquire and place order easily from countries whcih doesn't share common language.
For example, a report by China government found that people who want to do business hire an agent or use translators just to commuincate with local people.
Business people can save lot of money just by knowing that particular language.
In conclusion, although it may not be easy for people to learn other langauge, I believe it can help to explore the new countires and open a bridge between countires to export and import.
