In recent years, more and more people join universities or colleges after graduateing from senior high schools.
However, the university life is totally different from senior high school life or before that.
According to the concern of living at home or not, my opinions is followed.
As for me, moving away and living on their own while attending the university or college is a better choice than living at home.
In the late of student life, living outside can learn and acquire more skills and knowledge which you may not acquire at home.
Before entering the workforce, undergratuates not only have to learn the professional skills but the social skills and self care ability.
Undergratuates can learn or acquire these competence quicker if they move away and live on their own.
They need to do everything by their selves, such as go to classes, mop floor, wash clothing, and so on.
Therefore, living outside may learn more than living at home.
Healthy living Regarding the question: Exercise is important for our health, but are there thing that are more important, opinions among people are quite different. Since each one has his own preference.
For instance, I would like to say that money is more important for me than exercise, even regular exercises are necessary to keep health.
However, it doen't mean that I don't do any exercise at all, and health doesn't matter for me.
Due to stressful financial situation and high life expenses, I have no choice but to work harder to get more money to finance it.
Therefore, compared to exercise, I will prioritze work.
Nevetherless I usually do zumba workout everyweek to keep me fit. Since if I am not fit and always sick, then I also cannot finish my task as planned.
However, some may disagree with me.
For them,health has absolutely the highest priority.
Therefore, there is nothing else that is more important than exercise.
And such people usually have a very good work-life balance.
I like to exercise in my free time.
I usually exercise every day in the morning before breakfast.
Before the Covid I was going to the gym, but now, I am exercising outside.
I practice Yoga, so my main activities is for strench and cardio.
In my free time I usually read or wacth tv programs.
I've started to mark my free time time and to get some time only for me.
