Write & Improve is an online platform provided by the Cambridge Language Assistment.
It helps an English student (or learner in general) to improve his vocabulary and writing skill.
In my opinion It is very helpful and stimulating because, for example, it can check the written text and give some advices about it.
This direct feedback is good for a self-taught and for every English learner.
Moreover, W&I is characterized by many examples and models of a possible Writing test.
In fact, there is a so called 'Test zone'.
Furthermore, there are W&I workbooks, in order to train daily with different topics: from sport to study, from environment to technologies and so on.
These workbooks are divided by sections, which depend on the English level: Beginner, Intermediate or Advanced.
Who wants improve his business English, there is also a section called 'W&I Business'.
However, I don't like the restricted number of simulation of Writing Test.
Completing all the 'free' topics, the others are blocked.
If you want unlock them, you should pay.
If I were my classmates, I would start using Write & improve.
I recommend it to everybody.
Nowadays, video games are part of children's life.
These days kids grow up with technology and virtual games and its pros and cons.
As a parent our responsability is manage our children's time in computer and trying to schedule it.
Video games are actually a good way to develop motor skills and sometimes to learn lenguages.
It is proved that playing video games help to improve coordination, multitasking skills and enhancing memory; for these reasons video games are a good tool to get distraction and to develop children's brain speed .
Contrary, the abuse of these games platforms are negative to children who spend their whole day playing video games such as triggering violence, bad perfomance in schools and health problems like anxiety, obesity or stress.
Personally, I think that playing video games is a good resource to help kinds imporve their cognitive development however we have to be conscious about the abuse of these games and we have to control the use of these video games console to kids.
The future of Travel Nowadays there are already various ways to travel, for instance per busses, trains or flights.
It is already much faster than the way to travel in the middle ages as people usually traveled with carriages.
And it was very slowly and the travel was more likely limited regional.
Due to the dramatic development of technology and further travel demand of human, the future travel is expected to be faster, cheaper and more comfortable.
For instance, it is not difficult to image that typical vehicles such as self-driving cars that can fly, will actually be widely used in the future.
This new vehicle can be used not only for a short-distance trip but also for a long-distance journey.
Correspondly, the international travel will be more personalized and flexibel, since almost everyone could fly with his own car.
And this new change may decrease the usage of large flights dramatically.
Furthermore, the the Outer space travel with spacecraft may also comes ture, and the trip for human will not be limited on the earth anymore.
Finally, with the wide application of virtual reality technology in travels and works, it is reasonale to image that people will do the real trip less and virtual one more.
