There are many means of transport which have been used for generations, but they are becoming obsolute and replaced by technological advances.
I strongly believe that public transports and more environmentally friendly vehicles will be used poluparly in the future because these new technologies help mankind to cope with problems related to environment, climate change and the growth of polulation.
Firstly, using public transports is beneficial for both the environment and the economic situation of people.
For example, buses can carry a large group of people at the same time, which reduces the number of vehicles on the street.
This will also decrease the carbon emissions significantly.
Also, bus tickets are quite cheap compared to gasoline prices.
In addtion, this mean of transport also helps resolve trafic congestions, which will save time of many people.
Secondly, the development of technology also affects how people travel.
Bateries are now more efficient than in the past.
There are many cars which use electricity instead of fossil fuel.
People are realized how servere climate change is, so they will use electric vehicles to travel rather than the classic ones to protect the environment.
