It means have a calm condition can be boring after a while and stop making a plan for the future.
For example, for a few years I experiensed a situation which was without any problems, but after a while I realized that I did not any useful work for my future.
What is more, facing with the challenges and new things can open our horizon and improve the way of thinking.
According to a survey on Oxford University, liveing in the tough condition can develop the creativity of people.
