Having said taht, human beings like trying immortality to see the future.
As a result some perefer living calm and long to face with unknown events.
I think, this exuse can not be enough to forget about endevouring new changes.
In conclusion, although some prefer having a long life without any trobles, in my view, short life but full of new experienses, is more enthusiastic for people.
