One advantage of living on their own is that they have opportunity to be more independent and develop their manage time and organization skills, due to they have to be in charge of the payments of the rent, do their laundry, make time for prepare their food and do all other stuff at the same time they do well in the university.
Apart from that, some students can live in a house or apartment with other students so they can make good friends and potentialize their social skills, owing to living with other people there would be good and not really great moments which implies that it is necessary respect, learn how to solve conflicts, how to express differences but without damaging someone.
On the other hand, moving away from home sometimes is the best decision owing to many students live away from the university which means they have to commute long distances in order to arrive on time to class, which can be tiredsome after certain period of time, so bearing this in mind living near the university can be perfect for this students and represents an opportunity to have more time to their subjects.
Nonetheless, this choice can bring out the best of the students it also can bring out the worst of them, because living in your own requires effort and compromise to take care of yourself and accomplish your goals.
To sum up, living on your own has benefits, learning and challenges but it is a great experience and opportunity to prepare yourself for a near future.
Finally, I would say that I support this decision but everyone has the right to decide and evaluate which is the best option for her.
We can find boths, adventajes and desadventages of studying aboard.
If we talk about advantages we can find experiencing new things, being in a forgeing country expand your horizonts and makes you a more interesting person.
Also looks good on your resume because tell your employers that you are open to differents cultures and have the ability to be independent.
Study aboard takes you out of your comfort zone, give you the opportunity of create social network around the world and also learn a new lenguaje (and that is always something positive).
As a disadvantages you can feel nostalgia from home and if you are close to your family, they will miss you.
Also you can experice cultural barriers whith the lenguaje for domestic thins like open a bank acount or go to the doctor.
And what about if you dislike your course or because personal issues you have to return early and spend a lot of money.
Studyng aboard is high risk.
