I felt so good to be with my grandparents and siblings because they love me, take care of me and keep me happy all the times.
When I was there, I learned how to kind to the people around you, value them and take care of them when we can. Because we can not substitute them with anything on the world.
That is why, that holiday was an exceptional for me.
