University students are considered to be adults.
They can be in charge of their own lives nearly like adults, however, their main goal is a full-time study, not yet a full-time job.
Choosing places to live during their study is one of a crucial decision for them to make.
For students who choose to stay at home.
One of the reasons might be finances.
Staying home can save a lot of money on accommodation, food, bills etc.
Moreover, staying home can guarantee the safety of students and put their parents' worry at ease by knowing that their children are in the safe place and in their most comfort.
On the contrary, students who choose to stay on their own during their study at the university, can be more confident and be able to handle any obstacles that might be thrown at them during this time, money shortage, juggling study and part-time job, take care of their own basic needs such as food and clean clothes, to mame a few.
In conclusion, I would prefer to stay on my own while study at the university.
Because being on your own can teach you to be strong, ready for good and bad situation in the future once you enter a work cycle.
