Many young people believe that migrating for studies in universities may benefit them while some of them like to be with their family for support and help in education.
In my opinion, families are the supporting pillar for every student to achieve their goals and offer them a good environment to be successful in their life.
To embark on, adolescents nowadays prefer to go far from their home because they think that it could lead them to the better carrier.
They choose this way because they want to become independent and gain some experience facing difficulties throughout the process.
However, they can suffer from the homesickness.
Furthermore, being away from family might results in to be follow sexual or porno site which destroy their life at the beginning.
For instance, some students who do not have family to keep eye on them they have no fear of doing dreadful things.
Their friends mislead them to do some crime for their own benefits such as consuming drugs, or theft for the greed of luxurious things.
On the other hand, students who prefer to live with their family because they feel relax that their family is here with them whenever they need their support whether it is financial or psychological.
Family also protects their children to stay away from misdeed.
They not only provide educational support but also taught them good manners and how to interact with people, help others, being aware from awful activities to be successful in life.
Although, being alone throughout studies can make students mature enough to face life troubles, being with family feels them that no one will help them in crises or risks, To sum up, stay away from the family provides the happiness of being independent; however stay with family gives a great pleasure to be relax and follow family advise to deal with any problems.
