I agree with this type of requirement that students must complete some volunteer work in order to graduate.
I have three reasons to support my opinion.
Firstly, students get a chance to communicate with many people by volunteer work whom they have less oppotunity to.
By cleaning work, they can communicate with local people and by devoting work, they can communicate with weak people.
This is beneficial for students because they can understand many perspectives as well as broaden.
Secondly, students get a chance to improve their action by volunteer work.
It needs spontaneity.
Students have to be active for others by themselves.
This is beneficial for students because action is neccesary to promote in the future.
Lastly, students get a chance to gain their self confidence by volunteer work as they are appreciated.
This is beneficial for students because self confidence leads actions.
In conclusion, I agree with the requirement that students must complete some volunteer work in order to graduate with those three reasons.
