Currently, there are many people prefer to use computers and tablets to study.
Thick and heavy books no longer being use by the students to study.
Why students opt to use computers and tablets to study instead of reading books?
This is in light of the fact that many students think that using computers or tablets to study is more convinient than reading books.
Thus, a question starts to linger in every students' mind, 'should computers and tablets completely replace books in schools and universities?' .
As a students from my point of view, I think that schools and universities should replace books with computers and tablets.
This is because books are very inconvinient.
Books are very thick and heavy.
There are a lot of newspaper acticle alleged that many students suffer from backpain injuries, bone deformation and growth disorder.
Students ought to carry heavy and bulky books to schools or universities every day.
Thus, sooner or later they will suffer from these injuries.
On the other hand, bringing a computer or a tablet to school is much more convinient and students do not need to bring a lot of school bags to school.
They just need to bring one backpack to keep the computer or tablets.
This is the fact that all of the documents have store in the computer or tablets.
As all of us know that a computer or a tablet will not heavier that a stack of books.
Besides, one of my reasons to agree that computers and tablets should completely replace books in schools and universities is that when students need to search for some informations, they do not need to flip through by pages.
With a click of a finger, students are able to look up the informations by using computers or tablets.
Consequently, students are able to save some precious time and can reduce their strenuous study sechedules because they have more free time.
From my perspective, I truly think that using computer or tablets brings us a lot of perks and benefits.
In conclusion, I agree that computers and tablets should completely replace books in schools and universities
