Everybody should travel at least one time in own life.
Most people have already done it or not yet.
Concerning my own experience, I am going to spend some lines about my best holiday ever.
Two years ago, my friends and I booked a holiday, which would have lasted a week, three days in Praha and the other three ones in Budapest, Hungary.
I admit we were so excited.
Nothing went wrong, so we took off to Praha on 10th of August.
After that, we went to the hostel, in order to leave luggage and start our adventure!
Despite we had few days, we exploited them as well as we could do and we visited many typical places of that fascinating city.
In fact, we went to the Old Castle, we went into the historical centre , buying some souvenirs and taking many photos as memories.
Then, we had lunch in a typical restaurant, where we could have tasted traditional plates and drunk a lot of beer!
However, the best would have still not come.
This was when we went to the spa.
What a beautiful day!
Thanks to my friends, it was the best holiday ever.
