Everybody knows exercises are a significant thing to stay healthy.
There are different factors like food and sleep, of course.
Firstly, every people needs to do exercise.
If our body doesn't move sufficiently, it doesn't work smoothly.
We shouldn't lay on the sofa every time.
Consequently, people need to do exercise 30 minutes daily.
Secondly, foods are another most important thing for our body.
If we want to stay healthy, we should be careful about what we eat.
We shouldn't eat too many hamburgers, chips, and other unhealthy food.
Our body needs healthy oils, a sufficient amount of vitamins, and minerals.
If we don't take these beneficial things, our body doesn't work smoothly.
We don't eat at night because our bodies need to recovery at night.
Another significant thing to stay healthy, sleep.
Every person needs to quality of sleep.
If we didn't have a sufficient amount of sleep, we would be like a zombie.
A normal person needs to sleep 8 hours daily.
As a result, we should do these things.
They are simple and feasible to stay healthy.
