New technologies have been developed.
Researchers from the most famous universities of the world are still studying, focusing on new solution and technological strategies.
These are referring especially to the future of travel. Not only on the Earth, but also in the Space.
During the last two centuries, the way of travel from one place to another one has drastically changed.
The first industrial revolution provided new transport ways and tools.
Ships, trains and so on were the beginning of the Modern Age.
Nowadays, cars ,trains, planes and so forth are enhanced by using new smart materials and technological processes.
The aim of the most important factories of the world and aerospacial companies, such as NASA and ESA, is represented by succeeding in bringing man to Mars.
Concerning the travel on the Earth, many tests have been done in these years.
A very interesting one is the design of a 'flying car',which is able to carry passengers in the air, among the skygratings of the metropolies.
By the 2024 the first prototype is likely to be available on commerce.
This is the proof that travel is bound to be really different in the next future, becoming better and better.
