I was with my shool friends on a trip in Warsaw.
We started from Radomsko about 7 a.m. and three hours later we were already in our capitol.
We parked near old city so we could sightseeing Kings' Castle and Column Zygmunt III Waza.
From old city we should saw amazing views, especially of the National Stadium.
On the old city we spent about thre hours.
Our teacher prepared creative trial games and we must searched many places and talked with another people.
What is your favourite place on the old city in our capitol, Billal?
At 12.00 we could heard Warsaw anthem from tower clock Kings' Castle.
