We discussed about future of European Union, Polish place and position in EU.
What do you think about the future of EU, Billal?
Are you thinking that EU should more united and new countries have acces or not?
Returning to my trip to Warsaw.
After an appoinment wit NGO's we had a lunch.
Two hours later we went for a walk in the King's Bathrooms.
You don't believed me, Billal!
We met here President of Warsaw!
We could did photos with him and taught about important matters of our country.
I have recordered when he greeting our school!
You should see it!
We have been back to Radomsko at 9 p.m., tired, on the last leg but we have been happy!
Billal, I'm happy and enjoying from my trip.
Every activities was amazing.
It was a great time!
Write to me quickle, please!
Warm regards, Elizabeth.
