I think it is better for students to have the same teacher for several years.
Students and teachers all need time to be familiar to each other.
The is a period for each other to adapt.
If students change teacher every year, they will be alwasy spending time on the loop.
For teachers, it's important to know the ability, character and personality of every students.
With these information, teachers can then use proper method to teach different types of students.
For students who lack confidence in their ability, the teacher might create attainable goals.
For students who lack interest in studies, the teacher might use interesting way to make it fun.
There is one proverb, Teach students according to theire aptitude.
For students, it takes time to adapt the teaching style of a teacher.
Some teachers focus on the class communication, while others focus on the homework.
Students usually perform better after they are used to the schedule.
That's why I think it's a better way for students to have the same teacher for several years.
Nowadays we have two group of people.
One group prefers to lead a calm life, in small cities.
Mostly they try not so stress too much, therefore they live longer.
At the same time the other one chooses to have an intense life, with loads of changes, it provides their lifes with loads of fun and joy.
Nevertheless, changes are related to stress, what might be one of the reasons of premature dead.
According to personal factors everyone chooses, which one he or she prefers.
Living a long and calm life might be a dream for lots of people.
Even though following businesses and careers is popular nowadays, some people prefer to lead their lifes in a different way.
They prefer to spend time with their families, have a non-stressing job and enjoy little things they have.
However, sometimes those people might get bored and get into routine with their lifes.
Living an intense life might make some people feel happy, but for some could it be overwhelming.
I think enjoying each of the days and not being bored is a domene of people who have an intense life.
By doing something they love, they fulfill their passions and dreams.
Nevertheless, in some cases a high pace of life might lead to stress and disorders that might interfere with plans of living a long life.
Taking everything into consideration I think I would choose to live a longer without loads of stress, because I like being healthy.
