The school is one of the most important steps of people's life and it must be good for everyone.
For this reason, I think that changing teachers every year is one of the worst things of the school.
In fact, whith the same teacher students can be followed by a complete educational path that include also a straight school program.
When a new teacher arrives, he has to check the knowledge of the class and, in general, he must repeat plenty of things because he doesn't know what the students have studied or what was the previous teacher's method.
It's also true that changing teachers could be good to avoid bad professors but with an effcient school system and prepareted teachers students can really benefit from it with a consequent increasing of their preparation and general knowledge and establishing a great emphathy with who could be one of the most influent person on a student's life.
