In my opinion, during the time zoos are becoming dangerous for the environment.
In fact, in the last century, the environment has been damaged too much by pollution and by the elimination of green zones.
For this reason, zoos represent a dangerous way of alterating the natural habitats of animals which are, during last years, much less.
I think animals must be free of any type of artificial jails, that carry only the disruction of the normal nature life.
I think that in our digital era, animals can be studied and people can learn also by documentaries and innovative ways, such as videos or through the virtual reality.
Maybe somebody can say that zoos are useful to preserve the animals that risk the extinsion, but I think that they are wrong, because zoos were only made for the human's fun, without any consideration of animals' needs.
So, risky animals can be supervised into a specific area that is limited but preserves the natural habitat of them.
In conclusion, I can say that a world without zoos could be a better world.
