My reasons for learning English Nowadays more and more non-native speakers have learned and mastered English due to different reasons.
Most of them have done it for their studies or works.
On average, most of them have learned English in their childhold.
As I was a child, I have also learned English in the school.
However, English learning in the Chinese school is primarily focusing on passing the exam not on mastering the language in the daily life or work.
Therefore, I still need to improve my spoken and writting English.
And there are several reasons for it.
Firstly, I need to master English for my master program, since all my finance courses are in English.
And in two months, I must write my mater thesis in English as well.
Secondly, I need it for job seeking.
Since the finance segment is very international, even in Germany, job seekers must speak and write English and German very well.
Thirdly, according to my experience, If I have mastered English, I am able to communicate with my children in English and help them to learn English in the early age.
So They will not have the same problems that I suffer now.
