There is no doubt that earning money is crucial in our life, to grant our lifes necessities, as well as being healthy is crucial to do your daily jobs and chores.
Sometime you fall in a difficult buzzel of which is more important being healthy or rich.
Being healthy can help you being rich, since healthy body can do his own jobs efficiently, with out complaining of any diseases.
To achieve the goals which may be a dream of wealthy you need to have healthy body and healthy brain, since illen body can't do anything even if he rich.
The second reason why healthy is more important is that, healthy body can enjoy his time with his friends and family, and eat any kind of food he likes, while being rich only will not grant that you enjoy your time if you are not healthy and have some diseases.
