They are the times when everyone can go out and have fun.
It makes the city where I live crowded, bustling.
In conclusion, winter is my favourite season for 2 reasons: One, it has a cool and pleasant weather. Two, there are 2 holidays which I like most happens duing that time: Christmas and New Year. -
Nowadays, studying abroad is the best option and popular, however, it's hard for some students who has little or no-budget because they compete for scholarships to study abroad.
So we can see that there is the disparity between the high-class family and the low-class family.
The advantages of studying abroad are to improve your language skill and discover career opportunities abroad.
These advantages are more attractive for students who are low-class family from other countries.
It's because the difference between economics and socialities.
In developing countries, there are a lot of students who want to study abroad for their future because most of them are from low-class family.
In contrast, the students from high-class family can study abroad with their parents' budget and they don't need to compete for scholarships.
However, there are also disadvantages such as high cost, language and culture barriers and higher risk.
These disadvantages are affecting all foreign students, by the way, studying abroad is still the golden opportunity for everyone.
