Exercise and practice are very important to improve our skills.
For our body they are quite relevant, in order to keep it alway fit.
However, it seems that exercise is at the first position and all the other things are less important.
In my opinion, take care of our health is important but that's not the only relevant thing: several things get our life coloured.
There is no point in getting our body more and more stressed by doing exercises for many hours.
In fact, recent researches state that it is sufficient to work out from 30 to 45 minutes.
An excessive session might cause problems.
Obviously, we want to avoid them.
Not only is a physical exercise important, but also a mental one.
Our brain is essential for the whole human body as well as our heart.
For example, reading books or doing creative activities such as painting or drawing, are very helpful.
The last studies in some famous institutes have confirmed how many powerful these activities are.
What's more, they can be done in the leisure time.
During the week, It could be a good idea alternate them with the physical training.
