When I was younger, my group of friends started a short non-governamental organization in my city that called "Social hug."
As I live in Brazil and the brazilian schools don't require of them studants a certain amount of volunteer work, I did all the work in this ONG because I wanted to.
Years later - or nowadays - I can see how important was biullding this project and working on it.
I knew a lot of people who are my close friends until today and the best part of this is what makes us friendship to happen: the wish to care eath other.
Certainly, every volunteer work that a person can make will shake a lot of inner feelings out and make he thinking about the society problems, asking for himself questions such as:"where I fit in this societey?"
Why those people need my help?" "
What is the impact of my actions?."
In the end of the experience, I'm sure that everyone will become a better human being.
