It is very tricky to answer the question "are there things that are more important than exercise for our health?."
To be honest, I think that exercise is the most effective way to improve our health.
First, exercise keep your body fit and flexible.
When you do yoga, karate or just simple do the morning exercise, you must move and use many part of your muscle.
That leads to release the energy and reduce the unnecessary lipit.
At the same time, your limbs will be familiar with that intense trainning, then your movement can beflexible and you can do many things than before easily.
As the result, your strength gradually improves.
Apart from the physical benefits, you will gain a pleasant mental health.
According to an article written by a group of scientists at Oxford, exercise can reduce stress and help you to have better sleep.
As far as I'm concern, a person who frequently exercise has the positive energy and to be carefree than sombody doesn't.
Moreover, exercise is a cheap way to improve our health comparing to other ways like going to the health care centre or hiring a private doctor.
Besides, it can enhance our patience and self-managing.
In conclusion, exercise is important for our health in special ways that no method has.
Telling the truth is an interesting subject to discuss together.
In my opinion, it is important to speak the truth but everything always has two sides, the good side, and the bad side.
Because I think telling the truth is good or not is depends on you and also depends on the situation.
If you want to make others happy but you know the truth will hurt them and you don't want it to happen then it is acceptable to tell a lie.
As I think a lie with a good purpose is better than telling the truth but it's going to hurt others.
I think it is difficult to figure out telling truth or lie is a good thing.
As I said it is good or not it depends on you and also depends on the situation, so there will not be a specific formula for us to apply.
As I know people tell a lie every single day and when they tell a lie they are not even thinking about it.
So humans always tell a lie but it is a harmless lie.
In some situations you have to tell the truth because if you tell a lie it is going to affect other people in a bad way, telling the truth is very important in work because when you tell the truth, everyone in the work can know the bad thing in their job and they can improve.
In some situations telling a lie is better than telling the truth, such as a friend you just meet.
