AUTUMN: THE MOST COLORFUL SEASON OF THE YEAR If someone ask me which is my favourite season, surely I'm going to ask Autumn.
Autumn is a wonderful season for many reason: 1) It is the season when the leaves start to fall and the ground become colorful such as an artist painting 2) In Autumn are a great number of celebrations, like Bonfire night and Halloween that are celebrated in many countries.
3) Autumn is the season when the school start in many countries , and this can be really enjoyable (especially for parents).
Personally I love Autumn because is a warmth season and it feels me comfortable, and also because I love the color and the food of this season.
Furthermore I like Autumn because in my country, which is Italy we have a lot of celebrations and festival that are linked with this time of the year.
Autumn is the best season
