Well. for me I likt to sleep in a dark and quiet room, because this is my styl and I always sleeped when the night be quiet.
However, I also can to sleep when there is noise, sometime I was taird I can't feit anything close me.
Finally, I tyhink 8 hours a good time for mintal health, but some body like sleep just 6 hours.
In my opinion is best time to sleep is betwen 10pm to 5 am.
Sleeping is one of the neccessary things of humans.
And the sleeping place is an important factor that is directly related to your quality of sleep.
For me, I would choose to sleep in a dark and quiet room for some reasons.
According to ABC article, light will make you find hard to sleep.
You will have a feeling as if there was daytime outdoor and your biological clock make you conscious and active.
So, it may take you a long time to sleep.
Another element for a nice sleep is sound.
The atmosphere around you should be peace and qiuet.
Therefore, you won't be distracted by other stuffs and feel comfortable enough to be relaxed after a hard day.
I recommend that you should play some instrumental musics or ballad songs.
They are studied to have positive effects on the qualify of humans's sleep.
In a nutshell, I like to sleep in a dark and quiet room.
I like to sleep by being in a quiet room, but having a small light at the corner of the room because, i'm still a bit scared of the dark.
When I sleep in a dark quiet place it relaxes my mind from any problems or stress that I might have during the day.
When you sleep in a dark place your mind is more likely to sleep because of the lack of light, so I can have a good night's rest for the next day.
That is how I like to sleep.
