Vietnam is a country that is famous for many delicious dishes.
And the food I like most is spring roll, a dispensable cuisine in special occasions like Tet holiday, Mid-autumn festival.
There are many ingredients mixed to create the rich flavor for this dish: rice-papers, shrimps, meat, green onion, carrots, wood-ear mushrooms, salt, pepper, fish sauce...
And the recipe for spring roll is also easy.
You just need to stir up all the ingredients with reasonable amount ,and then put them in a rice paper and roll it up.
The last step is deep frying them. That's why it called spring roll.
I extremely like this dish because the aroma and the taste is so good.
Moreover, when I make spring roll, all my family member will gather to do together.
So, this dish not only mouth-watering but also full of love.
