Nowadays, some things have already been changing.
The way to teach is different of the way when I was a child.
We are living in a multicultural society, so everybody has the same oportunities to learn everything about their original religion.
This is the reason why we can overhearing people talking in different language.
It won't be a problem in the future.
We may use a small device fit in our ear to translate all the conversations.
Furthermore, we will have a micro-chip inside our skin and our fathers or teachers will be able to know where we are.
In the future, the most popular language will be Chinese.
Therefore, if you want to learn a new language, you should start with it.
