Report about my experience with Write and Improve I started to use Write and Improve a week ago.
Till now I find it very usefull.
I like that it is very easy to use, the menu is very clear, with tasks ordered by difficulty.
It has different kind of subjects with all kinds of tasks and that is very good because it makes you think and improve your vocabulary.
I like that it gives you feedback, corrects your speling and you have the option to change your work and make it better.
I also like that it shows your progress.
This is very good because it makes you do better next time.
What I don't like is that in the feedback, on the answer the question it doesn't show correctly.
Even if I answer all the questions it shows me that I didn't.
I will defenitly recomand it to my friends.
It helped me improve my writing and spelling.
I discovered Write and Improve during my english learning course, and I found it an excellent tools to improve my skill to write about different topics.
They are interesting for everyone, but prior to all I appreciated to see the feedbacks on my reports in few seconds, with the highlighted mistakes and an hyphotetic result of exam.
Then, you can choose your level between Beginner, Intermerdiate and Advanced, but it's possible to switch its each time you want: and, important information, it's free of charge, you have just to register yourself on the platform, without any ads if you don't want, nor requesting of informations about your credit cards.
With an account, you collect the results of your reports for each level on a graphic who evidences your improvement or less.
In my opinion this is the best instrument to check your ability to write about something quickly, if you don't have a physical teacher or a classroom; knowing that it's very hard to have them today, due to measures against the spread of the coronavirus, I recommend to everyone this useful tool to stimulate your mind to develope arguments in English properly.
Enjoy your course and write, then write again!
