I think having new teachers each year is better than having the same teacher for several years since it is unhealthy for students' learning.
Having the same teacher must be difficult in upgrading class.
We have been learning new things in every new grade and if the same teacher is teaching for four years, he can be insuficient about new subjects.
If you want to hear a specific reason from me: Our primary school teacher was the same person in first grade to fourth grade and my middle school teachers were different each year.
I learned more and harder subjects than the primary school.
In my opinion, teachers should have test lessons and students should choose them.
Beside this, I do not think everything about teachers; sometimes the students should do more practice themselves.
Finally, I can say that, having new teachers each year is better than having the same teacher for several years.
The best tool for improving your English What would you say if I told you that there is an excelent tool to improve your English?
There are lots of tools to practice any languaje, but "Write and Improve" offers free payment options, furthermore it's backed by Cambridge University.
Firstly, W&I is a free tool and almost all of its features are free as well.
You can find excecises for any levels such as begginer, intermediate and advanced, the tool gives you opportunities to check your mistakes and correct them.
I would say that as you know there are many tools to practice and improve your skills and W&I is an excelent option because you don't have to spend lots of money and time, however, it has extra features and if you want to use them, you have to pay for them.
what I like most of the tool is the ease and assistance to avoid and correct the mistakes, moreover, it has a large number of excercises to do.
I sugest that if you really want to improve your writing skill, then W&I is one of the best options that you could pick up.
You only need a couple of minutes every day to practice and I can assure you that as soon as you notice, your writing will have improve.
