Notifying the truth have not always been convenient for every person.
Correspondingly, they speak for the false instead.
However, several critiques have been made towards the act of lie, although the lie is classified as white lie.
Nevertheless, some people still think that white lie is appropriate to tell.
Firstly, spreading a dishonest information has always been judged as a sin.
This doctrin has been manifested in children's mindset since early age.
The reason behind this cultivation is religious purpose, which correlated with the concept of karma.
Secondly, a group of people also decline the act of lie since it brings drawbacks for other individuals.
Every human being will certainly feel betrayed if someone tells them a lie, especially if it comes from a close-related acquaintances.
In contrast, those reasons are broken by the advantages of white lie.
Despite the denial of white lie by some communities, white lie has been acceptable for majority of people.
White lie is believed to be beneficial instead of bringing disadvantages.
Parents lying to their child for the purpose of eating vegetables by having slices of vegetables hidden underneath rice is a case in point.
In conclusion, informing an untruth information is often unacceptable since it brings harm to other people.
Based on aforementioned information, white lie brings benefit instead of drawbacks, making it tolerable for majority of people.
