The communication between countries is primordial these days for sciences as well as business.
Besides, means of transport have been improving, it is now possible to travel worldwilde.
It is pleasant to be able to go to a foreign country and discover new territories and people.
However, it is sometimes challenging to get by without speaking the language.
That's why, speaking a language is a way to be embedded in a country with a different culture as ours.
To put in a nutshell, not only is it crucial to speak a foreign language for work but it is also a way to get by and to be embedded in another country.
