For long time, in almost all schools the students are required to do a volunteer work.
This kind of jobs allow to students to obtain some experience, but there are not many places which want to give opportunities to young people or do not offer a healthy atmosphere for them.
Firstly, the voluntary work has always been a requiered to graduate from any high school or University.
As a estudent this kind of jobs allow to get experience, tenangeers are able to apply knowledges that they have obtained from the school and they have a better idea about how is the working life.
However, for students select a volunteer work is not always easy.
The range of options for this kind of jobs is sometimes limited, the timetables are not comfortables, as a volunteer the student do not receive a salary and some companies exploit the students.
To sum up, voluntary works will always be an excellent option for students to get experience, but as something necessary to be able to graduate, the Schools should research for good options of volunteer jobs to offer to their students.
