My experience on studying in platform Write and Improve is being great and plenty useful.
What I liked on Write and Improve is the possibility of writing several texts about many subjects, that from housework to subjects about the work.
Other thing I liked was the correction process, which the Artifical Intelligence had a good accuracy, and inform me on gramatical errors that I commited and how I can correct them.
I also liked on fact that the Write and Improve had four levels along his workbooks, where this four levels are the beginner, intermediate, advanced, and business.
However, the Write and Improve had defects that I didn't like.
An example is the fail on examine if the text I wrote matched with the platform asked.
Many times I wrote the text correctly with the platform asked, but the system says that I wrote incorrectly.
After using the Write and Improve, I can recommend the platform without problem to my classmates.
You will enjoy it a lot.
'write and improve' is an online writing tool for English language learners in all levels of English including beginner, intermediate and advanced. '
write and improve' gives you topics to write about, and once you finish writing the topic, you will get instant marking based on CEFR scale; which stands for common European framework of reference.
In addition, 'Write and improve' gives you instant feedback about your writing and offers you suggestions on how to correct your mistakes and improve your writing - and that's what I most like in 'write and imrpove'.
For people who are proficient in English language but want to improve their skills in business English, 'write and improve' has special workbook for business English that gives you writing tasks related to English used in business environments. '
Write and improve' is a very user-friendly tool and everything is arranged in categories based on your needs; for example, if you are beginner there is special workbook for beginner where you can use to practise your English.
Furthermore, for learners who would like to practise International tests such as IELTS and Cambridge English tests, 'Write and improve' has a feature called (test zone) which contains IELTS academic, IELTS general training and B2 first which are offered on subscription.
the most imporant feature in 'write and improve' that I appreciate so much is the instant feedback that I get on my writing which has helped me to improve my grammar skills as well as punctuation.
Finally, 'write and improve' is an amazing tool to improve your English writing skills.
