Furthermore, the Write and Imporve is on line lessons so that you can exercise whenever you are available.
It is for free to exercise your English writing and speaking on line.
If you want to improve your English skills, I recommend you should try it.
Which is more important, be healthy or be rich?
That is the question that lots f people try to answer.
Some people think to be helthy is necessary be rich, but not always it is true.
Except when a person has same condintion, be healthy is not linked to be rich.
People have reached a long-healthy life, even living in underdevelopment countries.
So, what has been happening in these countries?
People can buy natural food, or not industrialized food, and it helps considerably i their diet.
Recent researchs shows us natural food is healthier and cheaper than processed food.
Other important thing is eating less meat and more vegetables, people that do it reach long life.
Although, it is important to say, people need to save enough money to later days.
Everybody knows elderly people require especific care, and it is expensive.
In summary, saving money, eating healthy food, less meat and more vegetal, and save money should turn you into in a healthy-rich person in the future.
Learning a foreing language is not only a requirement but also it is a competitive advantage in the inteconnected world where we live.
Furthermore, is it is well-known that English is the most useful and recognized language around the world, bearing this in mind many people are looking for methods and tools which help them to learn english quickly and efficiently.
Speaking personally, one of the best and useful tools for learners of English is Write and Improve a free application developed by Cambridge in which every learner can practice her or his writing in order to improve her grammar and fluency.
Moreover, this application gives you a topic and some questions or poits to develop in the text, after one writes the text there's a check button and automatically the writing is evaluated after that it appears the feedback, which comes up with some symbols so as to correct some mistakes or to improve some parts.
Additionally, this platform is mainly about writing essays, emails, letters and proposals, also there are different levels since beginner up to advanced and business level which you can tailor according to your level to get start step by step and going up and up.
In addition to that, the main features of this platform is the huge variety which is a boon for every learner so to prepare for any English certification, other feature is that at it gives you all the necesary feedback and a prospect level in which you are, this latter could be B1 or C1 or C2.
However, what I most like of this app, is the amiable design to use, the guides to write and the variety of topics after all these caracteristics are essential for a learner who wants to boost her writing skills.
Despite all its benefits there are some difficulties at the beginning, one can struggling to find ways to being a C1 or C2, also one learner can stressed out herself when she's run out of ideas to develop whithin the text; but nobody says it was easy to learn and get better in a target language.
So, It would appear this platform have its benefits and some challenges, nonetheless I highly recommend this platform for all learners who are seeking for a tool to write faster and better
My favorite season of the year is autumn.
I have four reasons to support the idea.
First of all, we can obtain good foods in the season.
we can get a lot of crop like rice, fruits, fish, and vegetables.
we are able to cook delicious dishes with these foods.
Healthy dishes make us keep better physical conditions.
Secondly, climate is special for excersizing.
Fall is not too hot or too cold to move our body.
If you play some sports, autumn is more suitable than any other seasons.
I also like to play tennis, and I can play well in the season.
The probability of getting injury is the lowest in a year.
Thirdly, we can study very well in autumn.
The climate also gives us a best condition to read books or learn something.
It is easy for us to make concentration to get to start learning.
The quality and efficiency of learning might be improved in the season.
The final point is that I have a birthday in November, so I used to get birthday presents from my parents.
I have emotional memories in this season.
I was given board games as birthday presents, and my parents and I played the game together.
We enjoyed the game, and it helped us to keep a good communication and a valuable relationship.
In conclusion, autumn is the best season to start new challanges because of the climate.
Thus, I love this season.
