Education is fundamental for the humanity, and so are schools which have a significantly presence in our lives in a professional way and even they influence in our personal growth, as a result as we advanced the schools need to change and improve in order to proportionate much more benefits to the students and the society.
Apart from that, it is mainly known this pandemic caused by Coronavirus has brought many changes in many aspects and areas from our lives, one of them is the education specifically in the schools.
Before we as students take classes in the classrooms interacting with teachers and classmates, however now we take classes virtually through platforms such as teams or zoom, hence that we don't have social interactions, we just barely see our faces, in fact we only turn our cameras on when we have to present final projects.
Despite, some changes are necessary and it stands to reason that we have to adapt to the circumstances is not so easy.
Currently schools have many challenges to face in order to not only maintain their tuitions but also to keep their levels of educations so as to prepared in better ways to students.
Additionally, it is importan bear in mind those studies which have been done during the quarantine about the academic performance, which show up students don't learn in the same way, they do poorly in academic and social way, also the academic charge has doubled which not only affects students but also teachers.
On account of this previous, the schools will have to be different in the future, first of all they must guarantee safety while learning, so they will have large classrooms with appropriate ventilation, they will reduce their room quotas, installs safety points with antibacterial gel and schools will prepared protocols in case of covid.
Moreover, schools in the future will have to install cameras which facilitate to the students take lessons from wherever they are, they will use more platforms to explain some topics and to reduce the workload to the teachers; besides schools will have to train their teachers so as give and teach better in this virtual modality, other thing schools must change will be the boards, these have to be digital in order to avoid touching directly and so on.
Definitely, schools will recreate their facilities and the way they teach, taking into account many strike features although the main purpose is to assure the students they will get the best preparation for their futures.
