Dear Sir and Madam I am Fred Yamada, live in the town for many years.
I heard that the town council is studying about bannning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants.
So I would like to let you know my opinion.
I have objections to the bunning.
Firstly, please let me know the reason why you want to ban the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants.
I think there are no reasonable reasons for banning the use of moble phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants.
I think that it is reasonable to ban the use of mobile phones in the concert halls.
Secondly, please let us know the reason why you want to ban the use the mobile phone in shops and restaurants.
I think that in shops and restanrants are not public space, but private areas.
Is it possible to restrict the use of mobile phone in private areas by law?
If owners want to ban the use moble phones in their shops and restaurants, it may be possible for them to ask customers not to use mobile phones.
Thirdly, if you implement banning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants, in emergency how to contact with the persons who are on public transport and in shops and restaurants?
In nowadays, we feel that mobile phones make our life more convenient.
So it is difficult to restrict the use of mobile phones by law.
I sincerely ask you consider the restriction.
Best regards,
I think that to always tell the truth is not so important, sometimes it is necessary to tell a lie.
I think basically to tell the truth is very important.
I think that the one of the most important things on business is the trust.
To grow up the trust with stakeholdres including customers, I think it is very important to tell the truth.
For example, if a vehicle manufacturer have some business troubles such as recall of their vehicles, in general, such company should approgize the customers and send a recall notice for all customers.
Such company will tell the truth of the reason of the recall.
The reason why such company take above actions is to keep the trust with stakeholders.
So I think that it is important to tell the truth on our business.
On the other hand, I think we have some situations that it is better to tell a lie.
For example, in Cristmas, a lot of children belive in Santa Clause.
A lot of children are looking forward to receiving presents by Santa Clause in Cristmas.
Although adults know that the parents give the cristmas present, most of adults do not want to tell the truth so that they would not disclose the secret of Santa Clause.
I think this lie is a white lie, a while lie will not do herm for everybody.
So I think that it is nessesary to tell a white lie in some cases.
