However, my idea of living is pretty different, I enjoy doing outdoor activities which makes me feel adrenaline, activities such as climbing, parachuting, skating, etcetera.
I am aware that some activities could be dangerous, but it is something that worthwhile, traveling around the world is fascinating as well, visiting amazing places in remote areas, tasting exhotic fod are things that everyone should try once.
In conclusion, each person has different ways to see the life and has different aspirations.
We should do whatever makes us happy, since my point of view, I would choose a short but intense live.
