Everyone is different.
Everyone preffers different things, is keen on different things.
Everyone differs.
There are people who would prefer to live a long, calm life until 100 years old.
But, there are also those, who would prefer a shorter life, but much more intense.
When it comes to me, I would defienetly choose the first option.
To be honest with you, I'm not really a social person at all.
I do not like talking to people too much, hanging with them, or even texting with them.
I am, what it's called today an introvert person.
Don't get me wrong, I'm not against people who prefer to be partying and chilling with friends all the time.
For me it's just a better option.
Let me explain why!
First of all, I would not enjoy dying in my early ages.
I think that nobody would.
You see, having a long life is pretty nice.
When you are partying or doing those type of things, it's really easy to fell into a bad group, which will hustly ruin you.
If you are not aware of it, you will probably start taking drugs as a teenager.
Maybe it will be more intense, but I don't think that dying before your 30s is an enjoyable thing.
Further going, when you live a long, calm life it is more likely that you will get more from it overall.
It is way easier to travel, experience things, enjoy life and simply live, when you are not stuck to a bad 24/7.
Sumarising, I think that living a long and a calm life is a better and safer option for all people.
Travel in the future will be more comfortable, fast, and safe.
With the technological advancements, people will have many ways to travel, including virtual travel to another place through simulation of desired place.
One of the factors that will impact the way of how people will travel is the Artifical Intelligence.
Artifical Intelligence will help the travel companies to understand better your travelers, also it will be used as a first attendance to customers.
Among the things I believe will not change are planes, trains, buses, and ships as the means of transport most used to travel.
I don't see another means of transport being most used than these in the future.
I need detach the spacial travel.
In recent years, we're see a growth of interest in that type of travel.
Companies like SpaceX and Blue Origin plan to transport people to another planets.
This will have a startling and thunderous impact in the world.
