The only problem that I found is the auto-corrector, due that I rather have a correction from a teacher because he can give you a feedback and help you to find the mistakes that you might have made and besides he can help you to find solutions to these mistakes.
However in general terms I think that Write & Improve is a good tool to practise your written English and improve it.
