In my opinion, I like to sleep in a dark and quiet room.
There are some reasons for my choice.
Firstly, I think sleeping in a dark and quiet room will improve the quality of it.
In the room like this, I can sleep quickly than a room with small light.
And if there is some noise, it will keep me be awake.
Secondly, I think if I sleep with some noise, I will be used to it.
And if I set an alarm, maybe I can't hear it since I always sleep with the noise.
However, when sleeping with no sound, not only can I sleep soundly, but also I can wake up in the first ring of alarm clock.
So, the reasons why I like to sleep in a dark and quiet room are improving the quality of my sleeping and waking up when hearing the alarm.
