Today, I want to introduce you my home town, Nam Dinh.
Nam Dinh is an ancient town.
Tran Dynasty was there for a while.
Nowadays, Tran's Palace is become Tran Temple, a really famous place with many people in my country.
One more popular location is Nha Tho Do.
It is right beside the sea, so if you come there, you also can enjoy lunch with fresh seafood caught of the day.
Nam Dinh is a small town, that's why you can go both these locations in one day.
In the afternoon, you can go to the city museum.
There is Cot Co, a historical place.
I think my home town is really a heaven of streetfood.
There are many kinds of them: banh goi, pate bread, nem nam, xoi xiu and so on.
Also, if you come to Nam Dinh, you can't forget to enjoy Pho.
Pho Nam Dinh is really famous all over this country.
In the evening, Vi Xuyen Park is a perfect place to take an airing.
The residents often go there to play and do some exersices.
These are also many things in Nam Dinh that will impress you.
Let's come and experience.
