It's astonishing how the combination of main seven notes can create different kind of melodies, which at the same time fit in our different lives' stages, such as when we are feeling under weather or having a really difficult time, there are some songs which either make us feel a little bit more relaxed or even motivate us to keep going.
Apart from that, music always is our company when we need to dance or sing in order to find a way to convey our thougths and feelings when the situations turns out too much difficult.
Besides, the music is vital to make memories with those who we love and care for; we hold bonds through music and every time we listen to that melody we can remember an special moment, such as a birthday, a date, a wedding, a dancing, or just a loved person's smile.
On the other side, a long time ago Nietzsche said "Without music, life would be a mistake," and I completely agree with him, if we didn't have music we would miss a way to express our feelings, we wouldn't be able to fully enjoy a great moment or we wouldn't be able to put in words and notes our sorrow.
After all, music is so kindhearted with us to allow us to create memorable times and to liberate us from such overflowing emotions.
Music was invented a long time ago, and music plays a really important role in our life from past to nowadays.
Nowadays music is important for our lives, you can see, music is everywhere, in the supermarket, in the coffee shop, on the street that you go to school or go to work.
In the farm in japan, you can see the cows also allow to listening music because they believe when cows listen to music, the cows become more relax and they will grow up effectively.
That are some examples of music in our lives, you can see, somehow music become a part of our lives, music can also help us feel more relaxing and comfortable, that is why music is very popular and there are some study prove music can impact children in the good way, help improve their Bain effectively.
Music also can help adult and old people improve metal and physical health, help them can go through in the hard time and more gain more forces.
In my opinion, without music, our live is very boring and stress because music is a part of our live.
Today's world, studying at university becomes more and more important for young generation and it seems to be a most efficient way to learn about life.
To my way thinking, studying abroad is much more preferable in as much as that it contributes you youngers to be wise adults in three ways as follows. The first and foremost reasons for my choice is that many students do not have a chance to learn how to manage money.
For instance, they do not get used to pay bills for electricity or distribute money to other necessary items.
However, a university student has to take attention to make compulsory payments, otherwise he or she has to burn midnight oil in real terms.
Another reasons which absolutely deserves some words here is that staying at home during university years means beating a dead horse.
I mean, studying at university teaches young brains something about life not only for landing jobs but also becoming a social, conscious person.
And it paves the way for taking these opportunities and having fun to take decisions without any interference of parents.
On the other hand, sitting next to lovely dad and mom provides the same life style as if being a student at high schooll.
Lastly, it will be worthwhile to study away from sweet home since it accustomes both children and parents to live separately.
For parents, this milestone causes them to be able to travel without any responsibility,i.
e.
freely.
For students, they can find good jobs in other big cities while studying and Interning at big companies.
In a nutshell, it is the time to live freely and take their own decisions even though they might be wrong.
With the aim of learning life easily students should study abroad.
Otherwise they will miss the boat.
