Music, could represent many things depending upon who is listening to.
For some people, music represents a way of express ideas, feelings, and culture.
To others, is a way of entertainment, or even could represent a carrer.
Also, music can be a way of life, and it involves many other jobs and activities behind that are complemented with music.
So yes, music is definitely important.
It does makes us feel energized, relaxed, excited, even sad sometimes.
As history shows, music is related to some of the most important events, as protests, war, a way of intimidating your enemies.
Music is one of the most effective ways of communicating, and without it, probably the whole world would behave and express so much different.
At last, think about how memorable moments that you have in your life, probably a few of them, music was part of it.
