Nowadays, people have acces to numerous information.
The variety of human preferences is huge and vast.
In my opinion, every person is unique, so everyone could have different options regarding his life.
I tend to think that a calm and long life is my desire.
On one hand, the person's behavior means a lot for his type of life.
In general, people have had their actions made depending on their attitude.
I would like to argue that it is crucial to enjoy every moment.
Furthermore, the most relevant aspect is to choose your own lifestyle.
If it comes to my feelings, I will say that I appreciate a calm life because of my character.
If you have an outgoing personality, you will probably tend to choose a more intense life.
On the other hand, as far as I am concerned, in general, humans wish a long life.
I would like to argue that it does not matter the longevity of life in a choice related to life intensity.
If I aspire to a peaceful and harmonious life, I will have this preference despite of its durability.
Moreover, people have their activities felt in a different way.
As far as I know, the more intensity an action is, the happier you are.
Nevertheless, a calm and long life could offer numerous pleasant activities which cand be equal with a short, but deep and energetic life.
In conclusion, human preferences could be so different.
A long and calm life can be always the best choice because you have the opportunity to make many extraordinary memories in such a lengthy and relaxed life.
