In my opinion, music has a important role in everyone's life.
First of all, there are several kinds of music, and each one can have a different impact on your mind.
For example, there are some songs which are made for sensitizing people, whereas other ones are made in order to lift the mood.
Another key point to remember is that a particular song can be part of a special moment of someone's life; therefore, that song has a special meaning for that person.
Some researches stated that a song can really change a life; for instance, it has proved that it can really help a person get out of a state of depression.
In sum, life without music would not be as great as it is, since the rhythm and lyrics can really have a huge impact on people's mind.
Music is definately important in humankind.
It indicates how our lives are going on from the past to present.
Human has learned human being through music and its lyrics ,for example, politics, religion, culture and love.
Music is one the crucial parts of our lives so it plays an important role to alleviate people feeling when they encounter tough situations or encourage them to show their true feeing in term of affliction or political issues.
That is the reason why that life cannot live without music.
It there was no music, life woulnd not be lively and people did have imagination or creavitity to create magnificent lyrics or songs.
As a result, it is doubtless that knowledge or riligious teaching are difficult to convey to people.
From my point of view, I decisively live without music because music always sooths my temper when I feel frustrated with my problems.
Moreover, It helps me to have more concentration while I am working or reading books.
