You shouldn't ingore the purpouse of the white lies.
I still believe that children should believe that they are recieveing christmast presents from a little jesus and that if they misbehaved they will be taken by a devil.
There is a complicated dichotomy in case of leadership.
Your people deserve the truth but on the other hand they should be spare of some deeds of your own boss.
It is about a morale of the team.
An extreme example may be on a sea.
Sailors in the middle of the ocean on their transatlanit voyage with not enough of food.
Should the sailors be informed about the siuation or should it be kepts secret.
Is the possibility of mutiny less important then the truth.
The only hope of survive is to proceed on and hold on with maximum effort.
To tell the truth is the opposide.
So this is example when the proper solution is not telling the truth but simply to be quiet and with that not telling the lie.
