Music is a way of expression, and can influence in people mood experimenting different senses.
People without music would not have a filter to express and share their feelings and thoughts in peace because music allows people show personal sides of them.
Music is important because it can determine the mood in place or the formality of an event because depending on the music played, people can behave in one way or another.
Music open a wide way of opportunities of experiencing new sensations in different places and knowing people with different manners.
For example, it is not the same the behaviour in a concert to the behaviour in opera.
Music allows people to experiment those kinds of feelings and environments from their different music styles, and the best part, it is not necessary to be an expert.
Life without music would not allow people create and find a place of expression, and they could not develop their creativity.
To conlcude, music is one of the best resources of people's expression.
