In my country, Myanmar, there are only three seasons, summer, winter and rainy season.
All of them have their own beauties and signatures.
And if I have to choose my favourite one, that would definitely be winter.
I really hate hot days.
Also, I don't like being wet all day.
Therefore, winter is the only season I feel comfortable.
No matter how cool it is, I love it.
Besides both my birthday and christmas are in winter.
So I usually get many presents and this is one of the reasons why I love winter very much.
Moreover, I always go hiking with my friends in winter.
As we all get christmas holiday, I can meet with all of my friends including other towns.
And going hiking with them is always adventuring and fascinating.
And the most important thing is that I met my first love in winter.
And it was very sweet although it was just a one-sided love.
And for these reasons, winter has become my favourite.
