Music- A part of your world The majority of people have different opinions about music and it's forms.
Some don't actually relish music at all.
The question is though, are there times when music is significant and vital, in instance for our psychohygiene?
Is it sometimes required and necessary to listen to music?
Certain people believe that the shapes of voice and sound are highly calming to our ears.
The sounds may make us feel better and pleased, even when we listen to them passively and don't really give attention to details, such as words of the songs.
Owning to that being said, it is clear that music may reduce for example stress, depressive thoughts, wrath, sloth and many other wrong emotions.
How would life be without music though?
Depends on what type of a person you are.
If you don't fancy music much, then you'd be probably just fine but if the case is the opposite, you might be in trouble.
In conclusion, it is highly considered within the humanity that music is an inseperable, necessary, essential and fundamental part of it and makes us feel great.
First of all, nowadays listening to music is becoming a habit for every human is living on this earth.
Also, there are different times that everyone listen to music.
For example, there are some people like listening to music before going to bed, because they are feeling relaxed in this time.
Furthermore, there are some human being like listening to music while they are studying because they feel more concentrate in their studying.
Besides that, there are some others folks who prefer listening to music while they are working in housework because listening to music bring them more energies to work.
For this reason, listening to music is gaining more and more place in everyone life, and attract more people to be depend of listening to music.
For instance, there are some people who listen to music while they are sad or anxious to release this pain.
However, there are som people who listen to music when they are in a good mood.
Indeed, everyone is living on this earth has a specific goal of listening to music, such as listening to music while studying, working in housework, and in bad moments.
Moroever there are different feeling that the people are feeling when they are listening to music.
Finally, listening to music brings mor benefits on this earth.
I knew that someone need music in their lives. While, I also think that not all people need music in our life.
Firs of all, music is not only a way to make life better.
For example, my hobby is running.
Thus, when I have a time or need to feel relax, I usually go to a gym and running by using treadmill.
While, I don't listen music if I have a time.
In addition, my husband also have other hobbyies without music.
He is a person who feel happy when he make new programs.
Additionally, music is not necessarily for all to live a life.
There are many indespensable things for our life such as sleep and foods.
However, we can live a life without music.
In fact, long long time ago, people lived a life without music.
Thus, I believe that music is not needed for our lives.
