When you start learning a langugae, you are going to find that each language has a certain volume of recourses on the internet.
Some of them have a little number of recourses because it is not that popular, whereas others have a huge number of them, because it is an important language.
English is a great example about the second type.
If you tried to learn English on your own, you will be confused at firtst, but I believe that I can help you a little.
Writing is considered to be one of the most difficult skills in any language, since it needs a correct grammar, punctuation, and a good vocabulray.
Another problem would face you is the need for someone to correct your writing, and most of the times that is not available.
Write and imporve solved many of my writing problems.
The website contains a huge nubmer of writign tasks, divided into three main categories: begginer, intermediate, advanced.
After finshing the task the site will refer to your vocabulary mistakes and major grammar mistakes.
The best thing about Write and Imporve would be that it gives the English learners a chance to write everyday for free.
I have been using Write and Improve for months now, I started practicing through the intermediate tasks, but I Improved, and now I am writing advanced ones.
