Are you musical?
Have you ever thought about how important music is for most people worldwide?
How often they listen to it or why they listen to it?
There are so many moments in life in which music is our sole companion.
For example, when we travel by car.
However, there are also many others when we enjoy music together with our friends, our family or even unknown people at live events, such as concerts.
Music is important to help us pass time while we wait for something, to cheer us up when we are a little bit down or to celebrate when we are a good reason.
The sound we listen and the lyrics of the songs have the power to make us change our mood, to feel lively and energetic or to calm us down.
Personally, I can't imagine the world without music.
I'd be like a forest with nothing but bare trees.
In my opinion, studying music would be an obligation in all schools.
And I have this opinion because music is not only an art, but also a way to improve the neuronal conexions of the brain.
There are multiples studies and researches which demonstrate this.
All around the world, psychologists, doctors, musicists and several other professionals get at these same results: Studying Musics is one of the best thing to raise the brain's capacity.
Musics also have the possibility to socialize people.
It is very difficult find someone who does not like some kind of music.
Whatever is the style of music, there are always somebody singing a music.
I imagine that music, in fact, is something really good to the brain and to the mind.
And, the best of all: Music is a kind of art which almost everybody may to learn since kindness.
Children almost always like music, be singing it or hearing it.
Or simply appreciating that.
That's for all this I agree with the idea of apply musics for all students, whatever be their level of learning at schools.
In my city, for example, almost all the scholls already inserted these essay in their curriculum.
I am sure that it only have the goal of to improve several aspects of the students' lives.
I had the happiness of learning Musics when I was a child.
In my school, those classes began when I was 10 years old.
Since I started stay involved with these essay, I never forget about how good it was for all my whole life!
And since I discovered the amazing world of Musics, I never let it anymore!
My suggestion about these essay is: Dear teachers!
Never let to apply Musics for your pupils! For sure, if you can to do that, all you will contribute a lot with the complete mental developing of many people in the world!
