Life choices In modern society, people can easily live to 100 if they live healthy lives, but most people do not live to 100 which means they have chosen not to live healthy all the time.
Understandably, it is not possible to always think about the future.
Firstly, humans are animals, therefore they cannot think of their happiness in the future, but of their present peace of mind.
So, people are not not always able to take bright decisions and there is nothing wrong with that as long as they enjoy their lives.
I would rather have a short pleasant life in which I had a lot of fun with than a long dull life and live to 100.
Secondly, coming back to the first argument, nobody will get happy from living a long wholesome live without any pleasure.
Everybody rather has a shorter live in which they have enjoyed life and they can say: "Wow my life was awesome man, i do not regret anything."
Instead of having a dreary live and they will say: "Well if I had walked 10 more steps ervery day, this would not have happend" In conclusion, I rather have a short, but joyfull life than a long but drab life.
Since, I will be able to look back at my life on my deathbed and think, wow what a amazing life I had.
