Now, I'm sure I can't live without music and I'm looking foward to the next Doja Cat album!
There are uncountable reasons for this problem.
And perhaps it can be very hard to find solutions for it.
Why so many doctors prefer to work in cities where it is possible to earn much money?
The answer: There are several reasons, and one can tell some of them: First: Those cities with many people are places where there are much more opportunities.
If there are much possibilities, there will be much more money, too.
Second: With more money in the pocket, it is possible to choose best conditions of life.
And the things are an unstoppable circle.
Third: Perhaps doctors want to work in the richest cities because there are more advanced technologies, more researches, more qualified people to work beside the Health's professionals.
These are only some of the reasons I see that preference.
But, what can we say about the real situation of those people who live in rural areas?
In these places, there is not enough Medical profesionals' area.
So, why those doctors don't want to work there?
Well, the poverty is a huge reality...
the places where those people have to work are simple and small, and they almost don't receive enough research or support to continue doing their activities.
In these smaller cities (or districts!),
these or that doctor uses to be the only professional to work during the weekends.
This means extra charge of work to several doctors, and, for these reason too, they choose don't work in places too far from great urban cities.
How can it be solved?
It is difficult to say that there is only one solution to solve this trouble.
In true, there are several points to be analysed.
It is necessary to give best remuneration for those profesionals that work in little cities.
And so, the Governments have to look with more attention to those people that live out of Capitals.
It is also necessary to improve the structures and conditions of those work places.
Perhaps after all these improvements, doctor can change their point of view and they want to change the largest cities for the calm from smallest villages!
