Mr. President of these Council: When it comes to improve the lives of all citizens, every decision is important and welcome.
Your decision to ban the use of mobile phones in some places is excelent.
However, I suggest only a changing when it comes to do it in some places, like shops and restaurants.
I will explain why.
Banning mobile phone in public transportation will be excelent!
Inside the buses, trains or taxis it is necessary to respect other passengers, and maintain silence, the maximum possible.
I think nobody wants to be disturbed by people who don't get to speak in low voice, neither by other who only wants to listen to music in loud sound.
So, your decision to ban cell phones in these places is really welcome.
In other hand, I ask you to reconsider your idea to ban them in shops or restaurants.
Think about those people who are all the time working, and the cell phone is their main work tool!
They continuosly are in contact with clients and several other people, and almost always do their activities during lunches or in a cafe, for example.
If that people can not use their mobile phones in restaurants or shops, they may have prejudice in their work...
So, I suggest to you think better about the restrictions that this Council intend to apply for all citizens, if it's possible, of course.
I guess that great part of this town have the same opinion I do.
And we believe that this point of view of ours, if can be accepted, will improve the lives of all people.
Thanks for your attention.
I've been using Write and Improve for a couple of months and it's definitely my favourite tool to learn English.
The plataform is filled with workbooks, you get to choose the level you feel comfortable with, wheter is beginner, intermediate, advanced or business, there's workbooks for everyone.
In your account, you'll be able to see every workbook you have done so far to see how much you are improving, there's a kind of score, from A1 to C2 that measures your proficiency and how you write a text from a topic that's been given to you.
Furthermore, you have a test zone with training to practice your english even more.
The website is helpful because we have a task help with a feedback that appears as soon as we finish checking our work and then they'll point it out the changes you should make to improve your english and have more achievements, they stimulate us to do even better every day.
We can see our progress through the years, I think it's easy and good for me because I already was in an intermediate level of english so it was not hard to get used to it and it's so helpful because I used to lack at writing and now I feel confident with my workbooks.
I recommend you to use it because it definitely will help you improve your english by showing ways to do it, with encourangement and tools you need.
