Offices workspaces Currently offices workspaces are a very important feature that can influence on the employees productivity and behavior.
Choosing which desing suit better to the workplace is so important than hiring the right person to do the job.
Enclosed workstations can be very depressive and some people can face these cubicles as a thretening space that can betray their creativity.
However, in the other hand an open desing office should give to the employees an idea that they can do what they want anytime, but just in case they are not familiar with that desing.
Open desing offices have been used in several industries and countries for many years and since it started, it has been working.
Although it is very important that this kind of office be used in the right way.
For example, it is a good idea using open desing office to marketing, sales, advertisement or another informal business.
But there are some industries where working in enclosed station may be necessary such as accounting firms, law offices and any fields where concentration and silent are an important requariment to the environment workplace.
Maybe own these two options could be a good idea, it would suit booth needs in only one office.
I guess it is very commun today.
Office buildings are been built with these two desings, whether employees need it, it will be available.
