dear Town council, I am a normal citizen in this town and I respect your oponion about banning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants.
But I have revesial oponion about this law.
I am a worker in this town for 10 years, i often have to go a long way to the work, so I think that I need to buy a phone for necessary situation, but the security on public transport is very low and I must to alert to pickpokets whenever I want to make a call.
Therefore, I see calling by public mobile phones is a better choice, I can move to the place where there are driver and bus attendant, it is quite safe.
Another reason for my opinion is that public mobile phone on transports and restaurant can support me in emergency, I sometimes forget my phone at home and I cannot borrow other phone, so public mobile phones are my saver.
Finally, the cost of public mobile phone's time is cheaper than private phones, so I can save some money for it.
As a labor worker, I need to accumulate as much money as I can, because the company only hires young man under 40 and will fire all the old worker when they are not effecient.
As you can see, I strongly protest your law.
Although there are some problems with public mobile phones like installation fee for we must put the phone on many roads, and the nuisance of being bothered by children, but we can solve it easily by ecourage people to use it more, and we can teach children not to do this, I think that is more benefical than baning public phone.
In conclusions, public nobile phone is convenient, safe and economic than other choice.
Sincerely, hang.
