In general that is not a good solution to bann something or a behaviour of people by using legal rule.
I prefer convince people of a right behaviour.
In this case Town council would like to bann mobile phones on public transport , shops and restaurants.
The difficulty of this rule is to be applicated and controlled.
The Town council must create a police squad to check if the rule is effectively applicated !
This squad will be source de tension between citizens, and owners of restaurants.
That is also stress cause between citizens. They will provoke fighting between us where police squad will be obliged to intervene.
All this situation risk to degenerate!
That will be better for the Town council to promote an preventive action.
Each citizen will be actor of this change.
It will occasion to promote new values of conviviality in publics areas.
The Town council will also promote places where you will use phone.
For exemple telephone booth where nobody will be disturb.
In fact this is a problem of education and the well being.
The Town council must introduce in a college class information about a good attitude in the area with your phone or other technology.
