Today, in Sweden, there is a huge variation between how much young people do sports activites.
Because of the negative effects on health of an inactive lifestyle, all univeristy and school children should be forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week.
First of all, it improves your learning.
When exerciseing, the blood flows to your brain and the rest of your body.
Studies states that you are more concentrated after been physicle active for at least 30 minutes.
This means that exercising on school time will help focus during lessons and therefore lead to increased grades.
Secondly, it helps to reduce the risks of mentall illness.
Mentall illness is a increased problem in our society.
Not only among adults, but also among children.
Lonelyness is one cause to mentall illness which can be avoided by joing a team.
When you join a sport team you will be a part of a group.
You may also make new friends.
Problems can be shared with a friend and make you feel better, and thereby improves chances of not be mentally ill.
I understand that not everyone will agree at first.
Why be forced?
My answer to that is that now we see a problem with many childrens inactive lifestyles and to solve that problem, we need to make it easier live an active lifestyle.
So, how could we make it easier?
To start with, I think it is neccesary to force students to join sport teams in school because then they do not have any excuse.
Children and teenagers will find a new favorite activities that will last them forever.
To improve learning, reduce risks of mentall illness and to make it easier to live an active lifestyle all university students and school children should be forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week.
Young people and sports Sports is fun, sport is teamwork and sports can be the spark you need to be active.
But today's day many people like students and school children are only gaming and not play around a pitch a repercussions because of that is that the health of those among us is getting bad very bad.
So the younglings among us need to be forced to do sports related activities for at least 3 times a week and this is why.
Health negativis The phenomenon of gaming has become a ordinary thing in today's society, but only not with some benefits most of the consequences are bad very bad.
Firstly teenagers who near the ages of 15 or 16 are having a bow in them posture due to staring hours and hours to monitor.
Another aftereffect of watching hours and hours to the same screen is that more and more children or students need glasses with the result that the prices for glasses are rising speedly
I believe that efficency should depend on the type of work performed by the office.
For example, an accounting office is not the same as an advertising office.
When your work is creative, the design of the space is an important part; colors, rooms to relax, have meeting with clients or talk with other colleagues are important.
You also have to think that some people work beeter in silence, others need music to be creative and all that elements must be considered in the design of the office.
Now, if we talk about a more routine type of work, comfortable seating and a good coffee station are elements to consider.
However, if we want to reach a real efficiency in the design of the workspace, we must talk to the people who work in that office, what do you need?,
how do you feel most comfortable?,
their pinion is important to determine if we let a mistake pass on the design.
In conclusion, together: workers, design experts, contractors must be listened to in order to reach an agreement on on design effectiveness.
