My favorite season of the year is autumn.
And it's not only because my birthday is in September !
I always had a deep connexion with nature.
It's the beginning of the end, the start for the cold days, the opening to Christmas days season and the new things to come.
In Autumn, in France, we begin the new academic year, so it's the moment to think about your future, your dreams, and preparing to achieve our goals and our ambitions.
Autumn means the fall of golden and brown leaves, the tiredness of animals preparing the hard season coming, the world slowing down, the trees reveals their naked trunks the leafy clothes which fly away.
It's the time to spleen, to dream, to walk alone and playing in the wind.
Memories of past years comes harder in this period, often memories from our childhood or our young teenage years.
For me, autmn is deeply linked to fearies and magic world.
It's in these days that I dream of being a fox or a wolf, and wandering in forest, in search of a little door from the magic land.
Dear Chris, It was overwhelming to hear that you could come along with my family to the museum.
We will get transported there by car.
Be aware that the car ride will be 50-60 minutes long.
You can find plenty of interesting things at the museum.
For example, you can see ancient fossils, learn about animals and their life cycles, guess if they are mammels or reptiles.
Additionally, you can also find out if they are warm-blooded animals or cold-blooded animals.
You will need to bring a plastic bag, your jacket, a notebook along with a pencil.
That would be everything that will come in handy.
I predict that we will have such a brilliant day spending time with each other!
Kind regards, Emmanuel Shapiro
