From: me To: Alex Subject: Party on Saturday My dear friend, I am sending this e-mail to you only to thank you for the invitation to the party next Saturday.
You are a great friend, we know ourselves there are many, many years, and I also know that you would never forget to invite me to this important moment.
We are almost brothers, and I know how important is this event to you, and I know what it represents to you, too.
Although this, I am using this virtual space to say that I will not stay present at this important moment of your life.
I apologise, because I even would like to participate of this moment by your side.
I'm so sorry for this, and I will explain the reason I will not be there, and I hope you understand me...
During this year, in almost weekends, I had been in several parties (including four or five with you, right?).
However, since last month I decided to focus part of my life to learn essays which can change my financial life forever.
I bought classes of financial education, and this has been my occupation last days.
I have classes on Fridays, Saturdays and Sundays, usually at night (two hours each class, at 7:00 p.m.). So, it will be impossible to stay in your party.
These classes are very important, because they are changing my point of view on money, finances, emotional inteligence, personal growing and several other essays which can change our lives forever.
I bought classes for an entire year, and their prices were so high.
We can say that it was an investiment to my life.
My focus at this moment is acquiring my financial freedom, because I intend to retire when I will be 45.
I know that this cannot justify my absence at your event, but I hope you forgive me.
Soon, I will be free again to stay in other events, and I want that you comprehend me.
It means that, for a while, I don't have any idea about what will be the next opportunity to stay in this kind of event.
Please, forgive me, my friend.
I sincerely hope that you might be successful in your event next Saturday.
Best regards,
