I almost advocate that computers should replace books in schools and universities.
At the present time, information technology and computers are increasing highly.
All of scientists and inventors always make attempt of learning or exploring about technology due to its excitement and change of the world.
In terms of laziness, nowadays humans are being couch potato and don't want to go outdoors.
Peoople don't have a drink and also read books in library; nevertheless, they decide to put their feet up, go to the Internet and read book online instead.
