All staff of business room have a discussion about what style of new room will be replaced in yesterday.
Two styles of business room are traditional rooms with enclosed workstations or cubicles and mordern rooms with open design will be decided by staff.
In my opinion, I think modern rooms with open design are better than other.
First, the most of company rent offices to working in the present.
The open design will help save space of working by expel thick wall between rooms.
Rooms are sperated by glass walls, mezzanine partition or panels.
We do not much money for renting.
Besides, open design mean that one room for all staffs, we do not need buy a lot of equipments for each staff, all equipments are shared by all staff.
Secondly, open design make an active environment of working.
Staffs can see each other so they can easy communication together, it make they feel like a team.
Finally, open design help raise effectives of working.
Manager can easy check what staffs are working.
Besides, staffs will limit personal job during time of working.
So staff will work more effectively.
