I have a dicussion with my parents about students should live with family when they are studying at university or they should move away and live alone in yesterday.
In my opinions, I think students should live with their family until they graduate from university.
First, students who are studying at university, have age between 18 to 22, they are young and do not have enough experiences about life, they are not clearly about social life, they are easily believe to stranger.
A lot of people are tricked about money by scammers or their friends when they are students in the present.
Secondly, students live with their family when they study at university which is a way to decrease burden about money for their family.
Students must pay a lot of money for four years studying at university.
Besides,If students want to move away and live alone, they must pay money for cost of living every month.
However, the most of student are dependence about financial by their family, so the most of money are paid by their family.
It is a great burden of each family.
They do not have knowledge about value of money in life and how hard to have it.
Finally, if students want to have independence about finacial when they move away and live alone, they must find a part time job to have money, The job is spent almost time of their.
They have not enough time for studying and joinning voluteer works.
It will effected to their learning outcommes in university.
