Music is probably one of the best things that people once begun interested in.
I think that almost everybody around the globe really enjoys time listening to music.
Listening to music started being a common thing throughout people lives.
Whatever people are doing, if there is a chance to listen to music while doing it, they usually do it.
People are listening to music while they are cooking or working out or just commuting to their destinations.
The fantastic thing about music is that it somehow can change people's mood.
Depending on what kind of music a person is listening to, it can make them fell happy, excited, energetic and also sad.
So even though people might be in a bad mood one day, music can change it completely.
Another thing about music is that In lyrics of music, there could be a lot of hidden sense that you could realize while listening to it and that could affect on you as well.
I think that our lives would be entirely different without music.
It would probably be a lot more boring and not exciting to do things without music.
People who make music would not be able to express themselves in music, and so they would likely be more closed to others.
Also, they would not be able to make money from music.
If there would not be music at all, the bad thing about it is that every moment of the live that contained music in it would not be remembered as good as it might.
Just listening to music could remind you a lot of things from the past, either it would be happy moments or sad moments.
I personally extremely enjoy these feeling when you get to listen to music that was playing at that time.
It is incredible.
From my perspective, the world without music would be definitely not as good as it is now..
