There are four seasons in a year.
These are spring, summer, fall, and winter.
The seasons are just the opposite in Northern Hemisphere and Sourthern Hemisphere.
For instance, if you are in Northern Hemisphere, summers are hot, however, the other Hemispere is cold.
The seasons have eccept on psychologi of people.
People feel sad and depressed in winter and fall.
They drink their coffee under their blankets by looking out the window.
During spring and summer, people become more active and full of life than other seasons.
I like being active therefore my favorite season is spring.
There are two reasons why I like it.
First reason is that the weather is neither cold nor hot.
The mild weather does not make you sweat or shiwer.
Second reason is that the nature renews itself in spring.
For example animlas migrate from the cold countries to warm areas, trees and flowers bloom.
All this change make people energtic.
Therefore I like spring.
