I have a discussion with my parents about does all university students and school children should be forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week in the present.
In my opnions, I agree with that ideal.
Firstly, the stroke sickness have trend youngly, the main cause of stroke sickness is inactive lifestyle. A new research in the sport mangazine show that anyone, who do not have enough or less taking exercise than 150 minutes each week, has stroke sickness rate higher than normal, so people should have at least 150 minutes for exercise each week.
In the present, the amount of young adult, who are students, have inactive lifestyle increase more than in the past.
Almost time of them are just for using the smart phone, internet and social online. The mobidity rate of stroke sickness at young adult increase every year.
Secondly, taking excerise make peole have a nice body, good strenght and good mental.
The scientist, who have main research about sport, show that people, who take excerise everyday, have life longer and stronger than people don't do it.
If you want to long life and healthful, you must take excerise everyday.
Besides, it help people relax after a hard working day, increase focus ability and intelligent of mankind.
Finally, students, who take excerise at school, have chance to trainning solf skill like team work, communication, making plan.
