Varied type of seasons has provided us to experience different sides of the year.
All of them have their own distinctive features.
For example; summer is known for its heat and holidays, winter for its snow and autumn for its leaves falling from the trees.
Fourth of them are good because there are in a limited time frame and they have been leaving their place to the next in the end.
But spring has always had a special place in me since I was just a tiny little child.
I prezume the reason that I keep apart it from the other is getting rid of the colorlessness and coldness of winter.
It won't show me that I hate that time of the year.
Especially snowy days and snowball fights are delightful.
But most of the time this is just not enough.
In the spring, the sun appears more vividly, revealing all the beauties of nature, the cheerful chirping of the birds reminds me that life goes on in any case and a situation can never be bad after the insincere weather of winter.
