People nowadays rend to be less active and consume more unhealthy food than they used to back in the days.
And as many researchers show that the fewer a person have activity during the day the worse their health are becoming.
And there is a huge problem with young population who are spending hours and hours a day siting at home and playing video games which have a negative impact on their health.
It is crucial to be active during the day and spend more time outside rather than inside.
Because human's organism didn't use to spend that much time inactive.
It used to have lots of activity and work during the day.
And now we need to find the ways to get people realized and encouraged to work out at least three times per week and spend more time being active.
But it is bad idea to force that people into doing sports activities because it may cause a big problem: they will be discouraged and obligated to do it.
And eventually, that may end up in them being fed up with, and they will give it up.
It is essential to show them that it may be not only good for their mental and cognitive health but also fascinating and worth-spending time.
The best way to do it is to build up more developed sports sphere that will provide people with lots of opportunities to be active and spend time beneficially.
For instance, the government may open up more gyms in the cities and provide them with brand-new appliances and good staff with lots of knowledge to train and encourage people to work out.
It is extremely essential to not force anybody to do sports activities.
They need to get encouraged and get willingness to do it themselves.
Otherwise, it may end up with bad results.
